%20the%20forgiven%20loan%20on%20ethics%20filings.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclarence-thomas-can-essentially-do-whatever-he-wants-scotus-impeachment-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20Justice%20Clarence%20Thomas%3C%2Fa%3E%20spent%20%24267%2C230%20on%20a%20luxury%20RV%20with%20a%20loan%20from%20a%20wealthy%20friend%2C%20but%20never%20fully%20paid%20it%20back%2C%20the%20Senate%20Finance%20Committee%20said%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F05%2Fus%2Fclarence-thomas-rv-anthony-welters.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20first%20reported%20on%20the%20loan%20in%20August%2C%20revealing%20Thomas%20paid%20%24267%2C230%20for%20a%20Prevost%20Marathon%20RV%20in%201999%2C%20or%20eight%20years%20after%20he%20was%20appointed%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20Times%20found%20that%20while%20Thomas%20had%20told%20people%20he%20had%20saved%20up%20to%20make%20the%20purchase%2C%20it%20was%20actually%20financed%2C%20in%20part%2C%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclarence-thomas-purchased-luxury-rv-with-help-of-healthcare-executive-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnthony%20Welters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20wealthy%20healthcare%20industry%20executive%20and%20close%20friend%20of%20the%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.finance.senate.gov%2Fchairmans-news%2Fjustice-thomas-did-not-repay-substantial-portion-of-267230-loan-finance-committee-investigation-reveals-failed-to-report-forgiven-debt-on-ethics-filings-raising-questions-about-tax-compliance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESenate%20Finance%20Committee%3C%2Fa%3E%20launched%20an%20inquiry%20following%20the%20Times'%20reporting%20and%20published%20its%20findings%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20committee%20said%20Thomas%20paid%20interest%20payments%20on%20the%20loan%20but%20n