E%3Cbr%3E%3Cstrong%3EAudio%20performance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20This%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20performance%20categories%20to%20evaluate%20when%20choosing%20the%20best%20Xbox%20headset.%20We%20test%20both%20playback%20quality%20and%20microphone%20quality%2C%20with%20a%20separate%20series%20of%20tests%20for%20both.We%20use%20a%20wide%20selection%20of%20Xbox%20games%20to%20test%20sound%20quality%2C%20including%20Forza%20Horizon%205%2C%20Starfield%2C%20Madden%2024%2C%20and%20Hi-Fi%20Rush.%20Spatial%20surround%20sound%20features%20are%20tested%20using%20these%20games%20as%20well.%20A%20set%20playlist%20of%20music%20and%20movies%20are%20also%20used%20to%20judge%20sound%20quality%20outside%20of%20gaming.%20Microphones%20are%20tested%20using%20in-game%20voice%20chat%20and%20third-party%20recordings%20from%20apps%20like%20Discord%20and%20Zoom.%20Recordings%20of%20voice%20chat%20are%20used%20to%20determine%20how%20well%20the%20microphone%20filters%20out%20background%20noise%20and%20how%20accurate%20the%20overall%20sound%20is.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuild%20quality%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20our%20guides%2C%20build%20quality%20focuses%20on%20what%20materials%20are%20used%20in%20the%20design%2C%20and%20whether%20the%20headset%20feels%20sturdy%20enough%20to%20last%20for%20years%20worth%20of%20gaming.%20Other%20factors%20are%20considered%20too%2C%20like%20whether%20the%20headset%20is%20easy%20to%20store%2C%20and%20if%20it%20offers%20alternate%20colors%20or%20design%20options.%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3EFeatures%20and%20connectivity%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EConnectivity%20is%20key%20for%20Xbox%20headsets%2C%20specifically%20because%20Microsoft%20uses%20a%20proprietary%202.4GHz%20wireless%20signal%20for%20its%20consoles.%20While%20all%20of%20our%20best%20Xbox%20headset%20picks%20are%20designed%20for%20use%20with%20Xbox%20consoles%2C%20we%20measure%20variables%20like%20the%20overall%20range%2C%20potential%20audio%20del