22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERep.%20Mike%20Johnson%20surrounded%20by%20House%20Republicans%20speaks%20after%20being%20elected%20as%20the%20speaker%20nominee%20during%20a%20GOP%20conference%20meeting%20in%20the%20Longworth%20House%20Office%20Building%20on%20Capitol%20Hill%20on%20October%2024%2C%202023%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%3Cp%3EWin%20McNamee%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20GOP%20Rep.%20Mike%20Johnson%20became%20the%20newest%20speaker%20of%20the%20House.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EHe's%20succeeding%20former%20Speakers%20Mike%20McCarthy%20and%20Nancy%20Pelosi%2C%20fundraising%20powerhouses.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EJohnson%2C%20however%2C%20has%20never%20raised%20more%20than%20%241.3%20million%20in%20any%20given%20election%20cycle.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20tenure%20as%20a%20GOP%20leader%2C%20former%20House%20Speaker%20Kevin%20McCarthy%20was%20a%20highly%20efficient%20fundraiser%2C%20sending%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20each%20year%20to%20PACs%20supporting%20the%20Republican%20Party%20and%20his%20own%20campaign.%20Now%2C%20with%20new%20Speaker%20Mike%20Johnson%20at%20the%20helm%2C%20the%20party%20may%20grapple%20for%20some%20time%20with%20how%20opposite%20Johnson%20is%20from%20his%20predecessor.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20its%20everyday%20role%20as%20part%20of%20leading%20the%20legislature%20on%20Capitol%20Hill%2C%20the%20speaker%20of%20the%20House%20also%20typically%20acts%20as%20a%20leading%20fundraiser%20for%20their%20respective%20political%20party.%20The%20two%20most%20recent%20speakers%2C%20McCarthy%20and%20Democratic%20Rep.%20Nancy%20Pelosi%2C%20were%20both%20fundraising%20juggernauts%20when%20leading%20their%20caucuses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPelosi%2C%20for%20example%2C%20helped%20raise%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fstory%2F2014%2F09%2Fnancy-pelosi-house-democrats-fundraising-110777%5C%22%