get%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrowth%20laggard%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECloud%20'optimization'%20continues%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20signs%20of%20weaker%20demand%20too.%20Late%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Google%20reported%20slower%20growth%20for%20its%20cloud%20business%20and%20executive%20Ruth%20Porat%20blamed%20that%20on%20%26quot%3Bcustomer%20optimization%20efforts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20shares%20slumped%2010%25%2C%20while%20Amazon%20shares%20fell%206%25%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20CFO%20Amy%20Hood%20mentioned%20these%20optimization%20efforts%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomer%20optimization%20means%20startups%20and%20other%20companies%20are%20still%20trying%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20control%20their%20cloud%20bills%2C%20even%20if%20they're%20not%20going%20bankrupt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThere's%20one%20big%20caveat%20to%20these%20concerns%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20generative%20AI%20boom%20is%20firing%20up%20demand%20for%20AI%20cloud%20services.%20In%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20startup%20extinction%20wave%2C%20some%20AI-focused%20startups%20are%20managing%20to%20raise%20healthy%20new%20funding%20rounds.%20And%20they're%20using%20some%20of%20that%20new%20money%20to%20spend%20on%20AI%20cloud%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20though%2C%20Microsoft%20looks%20to%20be%20the%20main%20beneficiary%20of%20this.%20The%20company's%20cloud%20growth%20was%20healthy%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%2C%20helped%20by%20demand%20for%20new%20AI%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Amazon%20reports%20on%20Thursday%2C%20we'll%20see%20if%20AWS%20has%20been%20able%20to%20jump%20on%20the%20AI%20bandwagon%2C%20too.%20The%20company%20has%20been%20rolling%20out%20a%20slew%20of%20AI%20cloud%20offerings%20lately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartup-extinction-wave-beginning-to-wash-over-cloud-industry-aws-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C