refresh%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20measured%20in%20hertz%20(Hz).%20This%20is%20a%20measure%20of%20how%20many%20times%20per%20second%20the%20whole%20screen's%20picture%20can%20update.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20if%20a%20screen's%20refresh%20rate%20is%20165Hz%2C%20it%20can%20display%20165%20different%20images%20within%20a%20second.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20how%20many%20frames%20per%20second%20(FPS)%20the%20game%20you're%20playing%20is%20going%20up%20to%2C%20you'll%20only%20ever%20be%20able%20to%20see%20as%20many%20as%20your%20screen's%20refresh%20rate%20allows.%20So%20if%20the%20game%20you're%20playing%20is%20running%20at%20100FPS%2C%20you'll%20need%20at%20least%20a%20100Hz%20screen%20to%20see%20it.%20The%20opposite%20is%20true%2C%20too%20%E2%80%94%20if%20the%20game%20is%20running%20at%2010FPS%2C%20even%20a%20100Hz%20screen%20will%20only%20display%2010%20frames%20per%20second.%20It%20can't%20create%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20refresh%20rates%20range%20from%2060Hz%20to%20360Hz.%20The%20best%2017-inch%20gaming%20laptop%20screens%20will%20typically%20offer%20rates%20of%20165Hz%20or%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20the%20difference%20between%20HD%2C%20FHD%2C%20QHD%2C%20and%204K%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20screen%20has%20a%20certain%20resolution%20%E2%80%94%20a%20certain%20amount%20of%20separate%20pixels%2C%20each%20of%20which%20works%20together%20to%20form%20a%20larger%20image.%20The%20higher%20the%20resolution%2C%20the%20more%20pixels%20there%20are%2C%20and%20the%20sharper%20the%20image%20can%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20find%20a%20screen%20these%20days%20that%20offers%20less%20than%20high%20definition%20(HD)%20resolution.%20But%20HD%20comes%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20flavors%2C%20ranging%20from%20standard%20HD%20to%204K%20and%20up.%20Those%20different%20resolutions%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHD%3A%201%2C280%20x%20720%20pixels%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFull%20HD%20(FHD)%3A%201%2C920%20x%201%2C080%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EQuad%20HD%20(QHD)%3A%202%2C560%20x%201%2C440%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E4K%20or%20Ultra%20HD%20(UHD)%3A%203%2C840%20x%202%2C160%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E8K%3A%207%2C680%20x%204%2C320%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%204K%20is%20the%20best%20resolution%20you'll%20find%20on%20any%20gaming%20laptop%20screen.%20Even%20that%20is%20rare%2C%20though%20%E2%80%94%20FHD%20and%20QHD%20are%20much%20more%20common.%20You%20can%20find%20more%20details%20about%20Ultra%20HD%20resolution%20in%20our%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-4k%5C%22%3Ewhat%20is%204K%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20explainer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20long%20should%20I%20expect%20a%20gaming%20laptop's%20battery%20to%20last%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%2017-inch%20gaming%20laptops%20feature%20great%20hardware%2C%20but%20the%20stronger%20a%20CPU%20or%20GPU%20is%2C%20the%20more%20power%20it%20takes%20to%20run.%20So%20even%20if%20you're%20using%20a%20high-end%20gaming%20laptop%2C%20you%20shouldn't%20expect%20the%20battery%20to%20last%20that%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20brightness%20turned%20down%20and%20power-saving%20modes%20turned%20on%2C%20most%20gaming%20laptops%20can%20last%20for%20about%20five%20hours%20of%20internet%20browsing%20and%20other%20non-intensive%20work.%20That%20goes%20down%20to%20about%20three%20hours%20if%20you%20turn%20the%20brightness%20back%20up%20and%20turn%20the%20power-saving%20mode%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20you're%20playing%20a%20game%20%E2%80%94%20even%20a%20simple%20one%20like%20Mini%20Motorways%20%E2%80%94%20that%20battery%20life%20is%20going%20to%20tank.%20Very%20few%20gaming%20laptops%20can%20last%20for%20more%20than%20two%20hours%20while%20gaming%2C%20and%20many%20won't%20last%20much%20more%20than%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-17-inch-gaming-laptop