Griffin%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20DeSantis%20to%20have%20a%20chance%2C%20Griffin%20said%2C%20he%20needs%20to%20win%20Iowa.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Chris%20Christie%20%E2%80%94%20the%20former%20New%20Jersey%20governor%20who%20counts%20billionaire%20Steve%20Cohen%20as%20a%20supporter%20%E2%80%94%20is%20done%20if%20he%20loses%20New%20Hampshire%2C%20Griffin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Citadel%20chief%20has%20been%20keen%20to%20find%20a%20GOP%20alternative%20to%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20has%20dominated%20polls%20despite%20multiple%20indictments%20and%20scandals.%20Griffin%20told%20the%20audience%20at%20Robin%20Hood%20%E2%80%94%20a%20charity%20that%20aims%20to%20alleviate%20poverty%20in%20New%20York%20City%20%E2%80%94%20that%20he%20believes%20there's%20a%20solid%20chance%20a%20candidate%20other%20than%20Trump%20and%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20wins%20the%202024%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECitadel%20declined%20to%20comment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGriffin%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20markets%2C%20as%20the%20hedge%20fund%20mogul%20is%20also%20the%20founder%20of%20market-maker%20Citadel%20Securities%2C%20which%20was%20valued%20at%20%2422%20billion%20last%20year.%20He%20said%20one%20big%20risk%20he%20sees%20in%20the%20derivatives%20space%20is%20the%20continued%20shift%20to%20passive%20strategies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20strategies%2C%20Griffin%20said%2C%20do%20not%20provide%20liquidity%20during%20periods%20of%20market%20turmoil.%20He%20played%20to%20the%20room%20of%20money%20managers%2C%20telling%20them%20%26quot%3Bwe%20play%20a%20very%20critical%20role%20in%20keeping%20our%20capital%20markets%20efficient.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20SEC%20should%20be%20thinking%20about%20how%20to%20increase%20both%20active%20management%20and%20ensure%20that%20the%20hedge%20fund%20community%20continues%20to%20flourish%20rather%20than%20continue%20to%20burden%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20