tre-on-this-date%2Farticleshow%2F104707812.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trudeau%2C%20Canada%20MPs%20Targeted%20By%20China-Linked%20'Spamouflage'%20Drive%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECanadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20and%20several%20other%20Canadian%20MPs%20have%20been%20targeted%20by%20a%20'Spamouflage'%20campaign%20connected%20to%20China%2C%20Canada-based%20CTV%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20this%20campaign%2C%20a%20bot%20network%20leaves%20thousands%20of%20comments%20on%20their%20social%20media%20accounts%2C%20making%20nefarious%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20despite%20the%20situation%2C%20the%20Canadian%20government%20is%20not%20acting%20steadfastly%20enough%20to%20take%20any%20further%20action%20over%20this%20'Spamouflage'%20campaign%2C%20as%20per%20CTV%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20statement%20from%20Global%20Affairs%20Canada%20(GAC)%2C%20the%20federal%20government's%20'Rapid%20Response%20Mechanism'%20(RRM)%20detected%20the%20campaign%2C%20which%20it%20says%20traces%20back%20to%20the%20People's%20Republic%20of%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20campaign%20started%20in%20early%20August%20and%20%26quot%3Baccelerated%20in%20scale%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20long%20weekend%20in%20September.%20It%20targeted%20MPs%20across%20the%20country%20and%20across%20the%20political%20spectrum%2C%20posting%20comments%20in%20both%20English%20and%20French%20on%20their%20Facebook%20and%20X%20accounts%2C%20CTV%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20deluge%20of%20posts%20claimed%20a%20critic%20of%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%20(CCP)%20in%20Canada%20had%20accused%20the%20targeted%20MPs%20of%20criminal%20and%20ethical%20violations%2C%20including%20the%20%26quot%3Blikely%20use%26quot%3B%20of%20deep%20fake%20videos%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Canadian%20government's%20RRM.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThose%20targeted%20also%20included%20Conservative%20Leader%20Pierre%20Poilievre%20and%20several%20cabinet%20ministers%2C%20but%20none%20of%20what%20GAC%20observed%20poses%20a%20risk%20to%20their%20safety%2C%20the%20department%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELiberal%20MP%20Omar%20Alghabra%20told%20reporters%20that%20he%20was%20notified%20by%20the%20government%20that%20he%20was%20one%20of%20the%20MPs%20who%20was%20targeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Transport%20Minister%20said%20that%20he%20received%20an%20email%20that%20reassured%20him%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bno%20direct%20threat%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20beyond%20that%2C%20he%20had%20little%20information%20about%20how%20that%20assessment%20was%20reached%2C%20CTV%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Alghabra%20said%20he%20did%20receive%20repetitive%20social%20media%20messages%20from%20different%20names%20and%20different%20handles%20directing%20his%20followers%20to%20see%20what%20an%20individual%20in%20Vancouver%20was%20saying%20about%20him%2C%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bcorrupt%2C%20and%20involved%20in%20a%20corruption.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20repeatedly%20posted...%20It%20clearly%20looked%20like%20spam%2C%20it%20looked%20like%20spam%20to%20me%20at%20the%20time.%20And%20now%20I%20know%20that%20it%20was%20orchestrated%2C%26quot%3B%20CTV%20News%20quoted%20Alghabra%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpamouflage%20is%20a%20tactic%20that%20uses%20networks%20of%20new%20or%20hijacked%20social%20media%20accounts%20to%20post%20and%20amplify%20propaganda%20messages%20across%20multiple%20platforms%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20Canadian%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20that%20monitors%20online%20spaces%20for%20foreign%20state-sponsored%20disinformation%20said%20the%20goal%20of%20this%20campaign%20was%20likely%20to%20discredit%20and%20denigrate%20MPs%20through%20what%20-%20to%20the%20average%20user%20-%20would%20appear%20to%20be%20organic%20posts%2C%20alleging%20impropriety%20by%20using%20a%20popular%20Chinese-speaking%20figure%20and%20silence%20criticism%20of%20the%20CCP%20by%20pushing%20MPs%20to%20distance%20themselves%20from%20the%20critic%2C%20while%20discouraging%20other%20communities%20online%20from%20engaging%20with%20this%20individual%2C%20CTV%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%2C%20Canadian%20Defence%20Minister%20Bill%20Blair%20said%20Canada's%20cybersecurity%20experts%20are%20working%20to%20determine%20the%20full%20extent%20to%20which%20Canadian%20government%20officials%20may%20have%20been%20targeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20bot%20networks%20have%20also%20been%20used%20in%20the%20past%20to%20spread%20disinformation%2C%20and%20the%20GAC%20said%20after%20reaching%20out%20to%20Meta%20and%20'X'%20to%20make%20the%20platforms%20aware%20of%20the%20most%20recent%20activity%2C%20much%20of%20it%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20being%20removed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20the%20same%20foreign%20interference%20monitoring%20system%20revealed%20it%20had%20detected%20an%20%26quot%3Binformation%20operation%26quot%3B%20targeting%20Conservative%20MP%20Michael%20Chong%20on%20Chinese%20instant%20messaging%20platform%20WeChat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20CTV%20News%2C%20Mr%20Chong%20said%20the%20current%20Liberal%20government%20-%20which%20created%20the%20RRM%20-%20has%20not%20done%20enough%20to%20protect%20Canadians%20on%20Canadian%20soil%20from%20%26quot%3Bthreats%20of%20authoritarian%20governments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20foreign%20police%20stations%20illegally%20operating%20here%20to%20interference%20in%20our%20elections%2C%20these%20foreign%20interference%20threats%20have%20disproportionately%20targeted%20diaspora%20communities.%20It's%20time%20the%20Trudeau%20government%20put%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20Canadians%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20CTV%20News%20quoted%20the%20Conservative%20foreign%20affairs%20critic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20affected%20parliamentarians%20have%20been%20offered%20a%20briefi