rorists%20may%20play.%20%26quot%3BThe%20number%20of%20foreign%20terrorists%20has%20gone%20up%20again%20as%20local%20recruitments%20have%20gone%20down%20drastically%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another%20officer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOut%20of%2046%20terrorists%20killed%20in%20the%20UT%20this%20year%2C%2037%20were%20Pakistanis%20and%20only%20nine%20were%20locals%2C%20official%20figures%20reveal.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%2033%20years%20of%20terrorism%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20that%20the%20number%20of%20foreign%20terrorists%20killed%20is%20four%20times%20as%20high%20as%20local%20terrorists.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%2C%20%C2%A0about%20130%20terrorists%20are%20operating%20in%20the%20Valley%20currently%2C%20of%20which%20half%20are%20foreign%20terrorists.%20%26quot%3BPakistan%20wants%20to%20keep%20the%20pot%20boiling%20and%20that's%20why%20they%20are%20pushing%20more%20and%20more%20terrorists%20into%20Kashmir.%20The%20fear%20is%20that%20those%20who%20are%20hiding%20in%20the%20upper%20reaches%20may%20also%20come%20down%20to%20the%20Valley%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20senior%20official%20in%20New%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20held%20in%20Srinagar%20was%20chaired%20by%20RR%20Bhatnagar%2C%20advisor%20to%20the%20Jammu%20And%20Kashmir%20Lieutenant%20Governor%2C%20and%20Upendra%20Dwivedi%2C%20Army%20Commander%2C%20Northern%20Command.%20The%20J%26amp%3BK%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%2C%20the%20Chinar%20Corps%20Commander%20and%20other%20senior%20officials%20from%20the%20military%2C%20state%20administration%20and%20security%20agencies%20also%20attended%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20nuances%20of%20security%20in%20the%20region%20related%20to%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20winter%20season%20also%20came%20up%20for%20discussion%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698258300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F4p6sr