0National%20Gallery%20of%20Modern%20Arts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDeclaring%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20saddened%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20inclusion%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bsacred%20model%20of%20the%20Sachkhand%20Sri%20Harmandir%20Sahib%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20it%20was%20presented%20to%20PM%20Modi%20by%20the%20Shiromani%20Gurdwara%20Parbandhak%20Committee.%3Cbr%3E%20%26quot%3BThis%20model%20was%20presented%20as%20a%20sacred%20symbol%20of%20the%20gift%20and%20blessings%20of%20the%20Akal%20Purakh%20and%20the%20Guru%20Sahibs...%20My%20humble%20request%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20stop%20this%20auction%20immediately.%20If%20the%20government%20feels%20unable%20to%20handle%20this%20sacred%20and%20priceless%20gift%2C%20then%20I%20request%20that%20this%20sacred%20symbol%20be%20kindly%20handed%20back%20to%20the%20Shiromani%20Gurdwara%20Parbandhak%20Committee%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20post%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20had%20announced%20the%20exhibition%20on%20X%2C%20saying%20the%20objects%20on%20display%20are%20a%20%26quot%3Btestament%20to%20the%20rich%20culture%2C%20tradition%20and%20artistic%20heritage%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStarting%20today%2C%20an%20exhibition%20at%20NGMA%20will%20display%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20gifts%20and%20mementoes%20given%20to%20me%20over%20the%20recent%20past.%20Presented%20to%20me%20during%20various%20programmes%20and%20events%20across%20India%2C%20they%20are%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20rich%20culture%2C%20tradition%20and%20artistic%20heritage%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20posted%20on%20October%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698256740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fvn25tvkg_golden-temple-model-auction_625x300_25_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgrossly-disrespectful-akali-dal-on-auction-of-pms-golden-temple-model-4514092%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Senior%20Akali%20Dal%20leader%20Suk