ight%20cross%20paths.%20We%20are%20a%20strong%20squad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUpon%20her%20arrival%20at%20the%20Sufa%20kibbutz%2C%20Ben-Yehuda%20reported%20that%20she%20observed%20the%20substantial%20scale%20of%20the%20Hamas%20infiltration.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20revealed%20that%20the%20combat%20between%20the%20female%20battalion%20and%20the%20Hamas%20operatives%20lasted%20nearly%204%20hours%20and%20included%20large%20firefights.%20It%20took%20about%2014%20hours%20for%20the%20IDF%20to%20secure%20the%20base.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20shared%20that%20the%20female%20soldiers%20under%20her%20command%20have%20made%20significant%20contributions%20to%20the%20war%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20more%20doubts%20about%20female%20combat%20soldiers%2C%20who%20have%20triumphed%20in%20every%20encounter%20with%20terrorists%2C%26quot%3B%20Ben-Yehuda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20present%2C%20we%20are%20responsible%20for%2011%20towns%20and%20are%20preparing%20for%20any%20potential%20ground%20manoeuvres%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20southern%20Gaza%20border%20area%20and%20the%20Egyptian%20border.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBen-Yehuda%20shares%20that%20members%20of%20the%20female%20troop%20have%20saved%20countless%20lives%20through%20medical%20care%20or%20by%20bravely%20landing%20helicopters%20while%20under%20fire%2C%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20commander%20also%20expressed%20her%20appreciation%20for%20the%20tank%20soldiers%20she%20led%2C%20highlighting%20their%20crucial%20role%20in%20safeguarding%20communities%2C%20including%20Holit%2C%20a%20kibbutz%20adjacent%20to%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20Tragically%2C%20during%20this%20period%2C%20at%20least%2011%20kibbutz%20members%20and%20two%20migrant%20workers%20lost%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20stormed%20into%20Israel%20from%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20on%20October%207%20and%20killed%20at%20least%201%2C400%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians%20who%20were%20shot%20o