ti%20Vikramarka.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20complaint%20against%20Mr%20Shah%2C%20the%20Congress%20told%20the%20EC%20that%20the%20home%20minister%20claimed%20in%20a%20speech%20in%20Chhattisgarh's%20Rajnandgaon%20on%20October%2016%20that%20%26quot%3B...Bhupesh%20Baghel's%20government%2C%20for%20appeasement%20politics%20and%20vote%20bank%20politics%2C%20lynched%20Chhattisgarh's%20son%20Bhuneshwar%20Sahoo%20and%20got%20him%20killed...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20further%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20pledged%20to%20bring%20Sahoo's%20killers%20to%20justice%20and%20%26quot%3Bin%20his%20honour%2C%20we%20are%20fielding%20his%20father%20Ishwar%20Sahoo%20as%20a%20candidate%20in%20the%20elections%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20complaint%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20party%20alleged%20that%20these%20statements%20and%20claims%20are%20in%20blatant%20violation%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20and%20the%20Representation%20of%20the%20People%20Act%2C%201951.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress'%20complaint%20against%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20Sarma%20pertained%20to%20a%20speech%20he%20delivered%20in%20Chhattisgarh's%20Kawardha%20on%20October%2018%20while%20campaigning%20against%20Congress%20candidate%20Mohd%20Akbar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20speech%2C%20the%20Congress%20alleged%2C%20Mr%20Sarma%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20one%20Akbar%20comes%20to%20some%20place%2C%20he%20calls%20100%20Akbars.%20So%2C%20send%20him%20off%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%20otherwise%20the%20land%20of%20Mata%20Kaushalya%20will%20get%20defiled.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20stated%20that%20Mr%20Sarma%20subsequently%20levelled%20allegations%20against%20Chhattisgarh%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20the%20tribals%20of%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20who%20are%20dear%20to%20us%2C%20are%20being%20encouraged%20to%20convert%20their%20religion%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%20And%20when%20someone%20raises%20their%20voice%20against%20it%2C%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20ji%20says%20'we%20are%20secular'.%20Is%20beating%20up%20Hindus%20your%20secularism%3F%20This%20country%20is%20a%20country%20of%20Hindus%20and%20will%20belong%20to%20Hindus.%20Do%20not%20teach%20us%20secularism%2C%20we%20do%20not%20need%20to%20learn%20secularism%20from%20you.%26quot%3B%20Congress%20leaders%20claimed%20that%20these%20statements%20and%20claims%20highlight%20a%20clear-cut%20intention%20to%20incite%20sections%20of%20society%20against%20one%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20complaint%2C%20the%20Congress%20alleged%20the%20central%20government%20issued%20orders%20directing%20civil%20servants%20and%20Indian%20Army%20soldiers%20to%20promote%20achievements%20of%20the%20BJP%20dispensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20acts%20of%20politicising%20the%20conduct%20of%20civil%20servants%20and%20Army%20soldiers%20violate%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20and%20the%20Central%20Civil%20Services%20(Conduct)%20Rules%2C%201964%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20party%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20also%20submitted%20a%20complaint%20against%20Govind%20Singh%20Rajput%2C%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20from%20Surkhi%2C%20Sagar%20district%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20sought%20his%20disqualification%2C%20alleging%20that%20he%20had%20publicly%20stated%20that%20he%20would%20pay%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20to%20incharges%20of%20booths%20where%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20votes%20would%20be%20cast%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20also%20submitted%20a%20complaint%20against%20%26quot%3Bunlawful%26quot%3B%20transfer%20and%20posting%20of%20police%20officers%20in%20Telangana.%20It%20claimed%20these%20officers%20were%20transferred%20before%20the%20completion%20of%20two-and-a-half%20years%20of%20their%20tenure%2C%20as%20mandated%20by%20the%20EC.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20complained%20against%20election%20duties%20being%20assigned%20to%20officers%20in%20Telangana%20who%20publicly%20support%20a%20specific%20political%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20has%20consistently%20highlighted%2C%20exposed%20and%20documented%20electoral%20malpractices%20and%20brought%20them%20to%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20ECI%20for%20action%20and%20redressal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThrough%20this%20process%2C%20the%20INC%20has%20ensured%20the%20deletion%20of%20lakhs%20of%20bogus%20voters%20across%20states%2C%20ensured%20the%20registration%20of%20FIRs%20against%20political%20actors%20engaging%20in%20electoral%20malpractices%2C%20ensured%20the%20transfer%20of%20officials%20acting%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20law%20and%20also%20secured%20campaign%20bans%20against%20repeated%20offenders%20who%20flout%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20said%20in%20its%20memorandum%20to%20the%20poll%20panel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Khurshid%20said%20as%20the%20electoral%20process%20begins%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20mudding%20of%20the%20waters%20by%20people%20from%20other%20political%20parties%20must%20be%20immediately%20curtailed%20and%20immediately%20put%20to%20an%20end%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20home%20minister%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Assam%20and%20other%20leaders%20travelling%20to%20different%20states%20have%20taken%20up%20%26quot%3Bdivisive%20and%20hurtful%26quot%3B%20issues%20that%20would%20inevitably%20divert%20people's%20attention%20from%20the%20issues%20that%20should%20be%20considered%20important%20for%20an%20election%2C%20and%20cause%20division%20and%20polarisation%20amongst%20the%20voters%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20have%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20and%20for%20people%20to%20be%20able%20to%20decide%20fairly%20and%20objectively...%20we%20hope%20genuinely%20that%20the%20Election%20Commission%20will%20be%20able%20to%20do%20something%20about%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20union%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFormer%20TPCC%20chief%20Reddy%20said%20the%20Congress%20brought%20to%20the%20EC's%20notice%20that%20elections%20%26quot%3Bhave%20probably%20become%20the%20most%20corrupt%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Telangana%20from%20the%20time%20this%20BRS%20party%20has%20come%20to%20power%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20requested%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20to%20intervene%20strongly%20to%20ensure%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698248880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fvi0on38_amit-shah_625x300_28_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-goes-to-election-commission-over-amit-shah-himanta-sarma-remark-during-poll-campaign-4513631%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20on%20Wednesday%20lodged%20complaints%20against%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20alleging%20that%20their%20remarks%20during%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20assembly%20poll%20campaign%20violated%20the%20model%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-goes-to-election-commission-over-amit-shah-himanta-sarma-remark-during-poll-campaign-4513631%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-goes-to-election-commission-over-amit-shah-himanta-sarma-remark-during-poll-campaign-4513631%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-goes-to-election-commission-over-amit-shah-himanta-sarma-remark-during-poll-campaign-4513631%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20To%20Partially%20Resume%20Visa%20Services%20in%20Canada%20From%20Thursday%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%