overnment%20%E2%80%93%20on%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20conflict%20is%20that%20it%20supports%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnegotiated%20solution%20resulting%20in%20a%20sovereign%2C%20independent%2C%20viable%20and%20united%20State%20of%20Palestine%2C%20within%20secure%20and%20recognised%20borders%2C%20at%20peace%20beside%20Israel%20as%20endorsed%20in%20the%20relevant%20UNSC%20and%20UNGA%20Resolutions%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20in%20a%20democracy%20where%20the%20right%20to%20protest%20peacefully%20is%20guaranteed%20and%20the%20government%20recognises%20the%20rights%20of%20Palestinians%2C%20here%20are%20a%20few%20instances%20when%20police%20cases%20were%20registered%20against%20protestors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20one%20of%20the%20first%20responses%20to%20the%20Israel-Gaza%20war%2C%20several%20students%20of%20the%20Aligarh%20Muslim%20University%20took%20out%20a%20rally%20on%20October%209.%20This%20peaceful%20rally%2C%20organised%20as%20an%20expression%20of%20solidarity%20with%20Palestinians%2C%20landed%20at%20least%20four%20students%20in%20trouble%20as%20the%20police%20booked%20them%20under%20Sections%20153%20A%20(promoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups%20on%20grounds%20of%20religion%2C%20race%2C%20place%20of%20birth%2C%20language%2C%20etc)%2C%20188%20(disobedience%20to%20order%20duly%20promulgated%20by%20public%20servant)%2C%20and%20505(statements%20inducing%20public%20mischief)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20soon%20after%20the%20AMU%20protest%2C%20directed%20the%20police%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Futtar-pradesh%2Fcm-yogi-adityanath-directs-police-to-act-against-pro-palestine-statements-posts-on-social-media-2725964%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etake%20%E2%80%9Cstern%20action%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20against%20actions%20or%20social%20media%20posts%20in%20support%20of%20Palestine.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20senior%20district%20police%20officials%20have%20been%20directed%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20Muslim%20clerics%20and%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20%E2%80%9Cany%20attempt%20to%20incite%20passion%20on%20social%20media%20or%20a%20similar%20call%20from%20the%20religious%20places%20will%20not%20be%20tolerated%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20cop%2C%20belonging%20to%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20posted%20in%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20district%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20had%20merely%20shared%20a%20pro-Palestine%20post%20on%20social%20media.%20Within%20days%2C%20he%20was%20suspended%20from%20duty%20and%20an%20additional%20superintendent%20of%20police%20rank%20officer%20was%20appointed%20to%20carry%20out%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Flucknow-news%2Fup-police-constable-suspended-for-pro-palestine-post-101697390625743.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Einquiry%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20about%20the%20constable%20and%20%E2%80%9Chis%20political%20inclination%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20similar%20incidents%2C%20the%20police%20in%20Kanpur%20booked%20two%20young%20Muslim%20clerics%2C%20Suhail%20Ansari%20and%20Atif%20Chowdhary%2C%20for%20posting%20content%20in%20support%20of%20Palestine%20on%20social%20media.%20While%20Ansari%20was%20arrested%2C%20the%20police%20raided%20Chowdhary%E2%80%99s%20residence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUttar%20Pradesh%2C%20however%2C%20is%20not%20the%20only%20one%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20protestors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Delhi%2C%20the%20state%20police%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Rapid%20Action%20Force%20had%2C%20on%20October%2017%2C%20detained%20two%20busloads%20of%20protesters%20who%20came%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9CCitizens%E2%80%99%20Vigil%E2%80%9D%20against%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20offensive%20on%20Gaza.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20two%20Fridays%20since%20the%20war%20began%2C%20Muslims%20were%20barred%20from%20offering%20prayers%20at%20Jamia%20Masjid%20in%20Srinagar%2C%20Kashmir.%20Police%20closed%20down%20the%20iconic%20masjid%2C%20apprehending%20protests.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EMirwaiz%20Umar%20Farooq%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20All%20Parties%20Hurriyat%20Conference%2C%20who%20was%20recently%20allowed%20to%20offer%20Friday%20prayers%20and%20deliver%20the%20Friday%20sermon%20at%20Jama%20Masjid%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjk-admin-lifts-mirwaizs-illegal-house-arrest-more-than-four-years-after-it-was-imposed%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eafter%20four%20years%20of%20house%20detention%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20was%20once%20again%20put%20under%20house%20arrest%20on%20October%2015%20and%20is%20not%20being%20allowed%20to%20step%20out%20of%20his%20house.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStarting%20with%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%20the%20violence%20in%20West%20Asia%20has%20so%20far%20claimed%20the%20lives%20of%201%2C400%20Israelis%20and%20over%205%2C100%20Palestinians.%20According%20to%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20Ministry%20of%20Health%2C%20about%2040%25%20of%20the%20Palestinians%20killed%20are%20children.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20the%20response%20to%20the%20protests%20in%20BJP-governed%20states%20was%20not%20surprising%2C%20surely%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20police%20in%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Congress%20states%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eare.%20The%20Congress%20condemned%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel%20but%20also%20reiterated%20its%20long-standing%20support%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20Palestinian%20people.%20As%20the%20conflict%20escalated%2C%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20(CWC)%20%E2%80%93%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20highest%20decision-making%20body%20%E2%80%93%20passed%20a%20resolution%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%E2%80%99s%20struggle.%20Party%20leaders%20like%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20spoke%20in%20support%20of%20Palestine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20actions%20were%20diametrically%20opposite.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Cubbon%20Park%20police%20in%20Bengaluru%20booked%2011%20persons%2C%20including%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Bahutva%20Karnataka%20(a%20citizen%E2%80%99s%20group)%2C%20and%20other%20unnamed%20people%20for%20holding%20a%20solidarity%20gathering%20in%20support%20of%20Palestine%20on%20MG%20Road.%20While%20the%20police%20haven%E2%80%99t%20booked%20them%20for%20%E2%80%9Cpromoting%20enmity%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20sections%20applied%20are%20largely%20for%20gathering%20without%20permission%20and%20for%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20nuisance%E2%80%9D.%20The%20problem%2C%20however%2C%20was%20not%20gathering%20without%20permission%20but%20denial%20of%20one.%20Almost%20all%20groups%20planning%20protests%20across%20India%20have%20been%20denied%20requisite%20permissions.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EProtest%20in%20Bengaluru%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Palestine.%20More%20than%201000%20people%20gathered%20at%20MG%20Road.%20Few%20of%20the%20protesters%20are%20currently%20detained%20in%20two%20police%20stations.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FBTMSWG8zJb%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FBTMSWG8zJb%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Prajwal%20(%40prajwalmanipal)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fprajwalmanipal%2Fstatus%2F1713907880334700868%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2016%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Mumbai%20police%20in%20Maharashtra%20went%20a%20step%20ahead%20by%20not%20just%20detaining%20the%20protestors%20but%20also%20allegedly%20beat%20them%20up.%20Two%20young%20activists%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ERevolutionary%20Workers%20Party%20of%20India%20(RWPI)%20%E2%80%93%20Ruchit%20Lad%20and%20Supreeth%20Ravish%20%E2%80%93%20were%20arrested%20on%20October%2013.%20According%20to%20the%20Mumbai%20police%2C%20RWPI%20had%20planned%20to%20organise%20a%20protest%20in%20the%20Matunga-Dadar%20area%20regarding%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20clash.%20The%20police%2C%20as%20expected%2C%20denied%20permission.%20Supreeth%20and%20Ruchit%20then%20decided%20to%20hold%20placards%20in%20the%20Lallubhai%20compound%20area%20in%20Mankhurd%20and%20protested%20against%20the%20Israeli%20government.%20Soon%2C%20other%20youths%20joined%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERuchit%20and%20Supreeth%20were%20subsequently%20arrested%20under%20sections%20353%20(a%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Essault%20or%20criminal%20force%20to%20deter%20public%20servant%20from%20discharge%20of%20his%20duty)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20332%20(punishment%20for%20the%20offence%20of%20voluntarily%20causing%20harm%20in%20order%20to%20deter%20a%20public%20worker%20from%20doing%20his%20duties)%2C%20along%20with%20other%20sections%20of%20rioting%20under%20the%20IPC.%20When%20the%20duo%20was%20produced%20before%20a%20Magistrate%20court%2C%20Ruchit%20alleged%20that%20he%20was%20brutally%20assaulted%20in%20police%20custody.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20they%20have%20secured%20bail%20in%20the%20case%2C%20the%20two%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20released%20from%20jail.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698247553000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25204156%2FF9LWbFmaEAAnGPB.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findia-palestine-protests-police-crackdown%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Curbs%20have%20been%20placed%20on%20gatherings%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20while%20some%20protestors%20are%20facing%20criminal%20action%20for%20acts%20of%20%E2%80%9Cunlawful%20assembly%E2%80%9D%20to%20promote%20%26quot%3Benmity%20between%20two%20groups%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findia-palestine-protests-police-crackdown%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Darfur%20Stove%20To%20Infant%20Warmer%20-%20US%20Award-Winning%20Scientist's%20Key%20Inventions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDr%20Ashok%20Gadgil%2C%20who%20was%20honoured%20with%20the%20United%20States'%20top%20award%20for%20technology%20and%20innovation%2C%20has%20always%20maintained%20a%20focus%20on%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20environment%20through%20his%20many%20inventions.%20While%20probably%20best%20known%20for%20the%20Berkeley-Darfur%20Stove%2C%20his%20contributions%20span%20the%20areas%20of%20water%20purification%2C%20efficient%20lighting%20and%20infant%20care%2C%20and%20have%20contributed%20to%20saving%20many%20lives%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20developing%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20Indian-American%20civil%20and%20environmental%20engineer%2C%20Dr%20Gadgil%20was%20conferred%20the%20National%20Medal%20for%20Technology%20and%20Innovation%20by%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20at%20the%20White%20House%20while%20fellow%20Indian-American%20Dr%20Subra%20Suresh%20was%20awarded%20the%20National%20Medal%20of%20Science.%20%26quot%3BTheir%20accomplishments%20advance%20American%20leadership%20in%20science%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20innovation%2C%20and%20their%20work%20inspired%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20American%20minds%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20White%20House%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Dr%20Gadgil%20spoke%20about%20his%20various%20inventions%20and%20also%20indicated%20that%20he%20is%20far%20from%20ready%20to%20rest%20on%20his%20laurels%20and%20is%20now%20focusing%20on%20preventing%20heat%20deaths%20in%20the%20developing%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELight-Bulb%20Moment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20the%20developing%20world%20was%20getting%20people%20to%20adopt%20energy-efficient%20lights%20and%20solutions%20seemed%20to%20be%20lacking%2C%20until%20Dr%20Gadgil%20had%20a%20light-bulb%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20a%20long%20time%2C%20it%20was%20possible%20to%20save%20billions%20of%20dollars%2C%20both%20for%20the%20consumers%20and%20for%20the%20electric-supply%20utility%20in%20the%20developing%20countries%20because%20the%20consumers%20were%20too%20poor%20to%20buy%20efficient%20electric%20lighting%20and%20they%20were%20receiving%20-%20%C2%A0most%20of%20them%2C%2080%25%20of%20them%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20poverty%20of%20the%20country%20-%20what%20we%20in%20the%20US%20call%20lifeline%20rates%20or%20subsidised%20electricity%20prices%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20innovator%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSubsidised%20electricity%20was%20not%20worth%20saving%20with%20full-priced%20efficient%20devices%20and%20that%20hurt%20everybody%20because%20more%20electricity%20was%20used%2C%20which%20means%20fewer%20homes%20were%20electrified.%20And%20the%20utility%20kept%20on%20losing%20money%20on%20the%20subsidy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20solution%20Dr%20Gadgil%20came%20up%20with%20was%20to%20have%20the%20utilities%20participate%20in%20the%20market%20and%20subsidise%20electric%20efficient%20lighting%20devices%20rather%20than%20subsidising%20electricity.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20nobody%20had%20thought%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%20To%20Darfur%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Berkeley-Darfur%20stove%20is%20a%20low-cost%20natural%20convection%20stove%2C%20which%20is%20very%20efficient%20and%20ensured%20that%20women%20in%20western%20Sudan's%20Darfur%20saved%20over%20%241%2C500%20(approximately%20Rs%201.25%20lakh)%20a%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20how%20much%20did%20the%20stove%20cost%3F%20%26quot%3BIt%20cost%20%2420%20(Rs%201%2C660%20approx)%20fully%20assembled%20and%20transported%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20Africa.%20We%20had%20to%20improve%20the%20combustion%20efficiency%20of%20the%20wood%20and%20we%20had%20to%20improve%20the%20heat-transfer%20efficiency%20of%20the%20fire%20into%20the%20pot.%20And%20both%20of%20these%20together%20is%20what%20allowed%20much%20less%20fuel%20use.%20The%20key%20was%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20it%20worked%20with%20their%20pots%2C%20their%20fuel%2C%20their%20cooking%20methods%20and%20still%20was%20inexpensive%20and%20easy%20to%20assemble%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20Gadgil.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20stoves%20were%20made%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20shipped%20to%20Africa%20and%20assembled%20by%20Darfur%20refugees'%20own%20labour%20and%20they%20were%20paid%20for%20the%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUV%20Water%20Disinfection%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Dr%20Gadgil's%20inventions%20that%20saved%20lives%20was%20a%20low-cost%20UV-filtration-based%20water%20disinfection%20system.%20The%20scientist%20said%20the%20focus%20was%20on%20disinfecting%20drinking%20water%20at%20a%20price%20local%20people%20could%20afford.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20big%20innovation%20was%20to%20look%20for%20something%20that%20will%20disinfect%20the%20water%20really%2C%20really%2C%20cheaply%2C%20but%20will%20also%20have%20no%20moving%20parts%2C%20will%20have%20nothing%20to%20foul%2C%20will%20be%20easy%20to%20maintain%20in%20the%20field%20in%20the%20developing%20world%2C%20in%20the%20rural%20context%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20scientist%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20came%20up%20with%20was%20a%20way%20to%20disinfect%20with%20Ultraviolet-C%20light%2C%20which%20actually%20destroys%20the%20DNA%20of%20the%20pathogen%2C%20but%20keep%20the%20light%20away%20from%20the%20water%20without%20having%20to%20use%20glass%20leaves%2C%20by%20suspending%20it%20in%20the%20air%2C%20so%20there%20is%20only%20an%20air%20gap%20between%20the%20lamp%20and%20the%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Gadgil%20added%20that%20making%20selling%20this%20water%20profitable%20ensured%20that%20people%20made%20some%20money%20and%20saved%20lives%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERemoving%20Arsenic%20With%20Electricity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20innovation%20was%20the%20low-cost%20technology%20to%20remove%20arsenic%20from%20drinking%20water%20which%20was%20invented%20specifically%20keeping%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20in%20mind.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20technology%20is%20based%20on%20releasing%20a%20kind%20of%20iron%20rust%20into%20the%20water%20with%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20electric%20current...%20and%20that%20dissolved%20rust%20captures%20arsenic%20and%20settles%20out%2C%20leaving%20the%20water%20safe%20to%20drink.%20We%20have%20two%20plants%20licensed%20by%20the%20university%20operating%20in%20India%20now%2C%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20scientist%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExpanding%20the%20scope%20of%20his%20work%2C%20Dr%20Gadgil%20also%20contributed%20to%20a%20%24100%20plant-based%20non-electric%20infant%20warmer%20to%20avoid%20infant%20deaths%20from%20hypothermia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAbout%201%20million%20infants%20die%20in%20the%20first%20days%20of%20their%20birth%20from%20hypothermia.%20The%20places%20where%20they%20die%20do%20not%20have%20reliable%20electricity.%20The%20infant%20warmer%20has%20reduced%20all-cause%20deaths%20of%20neo-natals%20by%20a%20factor%20of%20three%20for%20a%20large%20trial%20in%20Rwanda%20public%20hospitals.%20That's%20a%20very%20dramatic%20impact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETinker%2C%20Tailor%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20what%20he%20does%20in%20his%20free%20time%20and%20if%20he%20is%20hands-on%20and%20a%20tinkerer%2C%20Dr%20Gadgil%20replied%20in%20the%20affirmative%20and%20said%20working%20with%20his%20hands%20gives%20him%20concrete%20ideas%20on%20what%20could%20be%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Gadgil%20said%20he%20is%20now%20thinking%20about%20how%20to%20avoid%20a%20large%20number%20of%20heat%20deaths%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20are%20coming%20to%20the%20developing%20world%20faster%20than%20anybody%20is%20ready%20for%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20heat%20deaths%20are%20coming%20because%20of%20climate%20change%20effects%20and%20we%20are%20going%20to%20exceed%20survival%20temperatures%20around%20the%20world%20in%20the%20developing%20world%20because%20we%20are%20in%20the%20hot%20part%20of%20the%20world%20and%20people%20aren't%20ready%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Gadgil%20emphasised.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698247500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fn5l8gsu_dr-ashok-gadgil-650_625x300_25_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdarfur-stove-to-infant-warmer-us-award-winning-scientists-key-inventions-4513614%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Ashok%20Gadgil%2C%20who%20was%20honoured%20with%20the%20United%20States'%20top%20award%20for%20technology%20and%20innovation%2C%20has%20always%20maintained%20a%20focus%20on%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20environment%20through%20his%20many%20inventions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdarfur-stove-to-infant-warmer-us-award-winning-scientists-key-inventions-4513614%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdarfur-stove-to-infant-warmer-us-award-winning-scientists-key-inventions-4513614%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdarfur-stove-to-infant-warmer-us-award-winning-scientists-key-inventions-4513614%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kenyan%20soldier%20killed%20in%20DRC%3A%20Regional%20force%20source%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%2