2%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20partially%20resume%20visa%20services%20in%20Canada%20--%20closed%20last%20month%20amid%20a%20diplomatic%20row%20--%20from%20October%2026%2C%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commission%20in%20Ottawa%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%20Services%20will%20resume%20for%20entry%20visa%2C%20business%20visa%2C%20medical%20visa%2C%20and%20conference%20visa%2C%20the%20High%20Commission%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFurther%20decisions%2C%20as%20appropriate%2C%20would%20be%20intimated%20based%20on%20continuing%20evaluation%20of%20the%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20media%20statement%20from%20the%20High%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20visa%20services%20were%20suspended%20towards%20September-end%20as%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20nations%20faced%20severe%20strain%20following%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20allegations%20of%20%26quot%3Bpotential%26quot%3B%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20agents%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20who%20was%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20banned%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20and%20one%20of%20India's%20most-wanted%20terrorists.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20foreign%20minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20visa%20services%20to%20Canada%20could%20resume%20if%20India%20sees%20progress%20in%20the%20safety%20of%20Indian%20diplomats%20in%20Canada.%20It%20had%20attributed%20the%20suspension%20to%20%26quot%3Bsafety%20and%20security%20considerations%26quot%3B%20--%20a%20point%20the%20media%20statement%20underscored.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20see%20progress%20in%20safety%20of%20our%20diplomats%20in%20Canada%2C%20we%20would%20like%20to%20resume%20issuance%20of%20visas%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20diplomatic%20row%2C%20that%20escalated%20to%20involve%20tit-for-tat%20withdrawal%20of%20High%20Commission%20officials%2C%20snowballed%20after%20Mr%20Trudeau's%20comment%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20G20%20conference%20in%20Delhi.%20Canada%20will%20always%20%26quot%3Bdefend%20freedom%20of%20expression...%20conscience%20and%20peaceful%20protest%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Trudeau%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERefuting%20the%20allegations%20about%20the%20killing%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20s%20%26quot%3Bpolitically%20motivated%26quot%3B%2C%20India%20said%20Canada%20should%20share%20evidence%20to%20support%20their%20claims%20--%20a%20request%20Ottawa%20has%20so%20far%20declined.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698247020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F122o7v0g_modi-trudeau-afp_625x300_23_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-resumes-some-visa-services-in-canada-month-after-suspending-them-4513392%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20will%20partially%20resume%20visa%20services%20in%20Canada%20--%20closed%20last%20month%20amid%20a%20diplomatic%20row%20--%20from%20October%2026%2C%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commission%20in%20Ottawa%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-resumes-some-visa-services-in-canada-month-after-suspending-them-4513392%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-resumes-some-visa-services-in-canada-month-after-suspending-them-4513392%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-resumes-some-visa-services-in-canada-month-after-suspending-them-4513392%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Karan%20reveals%20if%20he%20will%20work%20with%20Kartik%20again%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698246944000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104704932%2Cimgsize-30508.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkaran-johar-reveals-if-he-w