panies%2Fnews%2Fhmd-global-expects-25-30-sales-growth-in-nokia-phones-with-easy-pay-launch-123102501108_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhmd-global-expects-25-30-sales-growth-in-nokia-phones-with-easy-pay-launch-123102501108_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Hurricane%20Otis%20wrecks%20havoc%20in%20Mexico%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698246190000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FE21A%2Fproduction%2F_131528875_p0gnqdzd.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-67216467%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20hurricane%20brought%20wind%20speeds%20of%20up%20to%20165mph%20(270km%2Fh)%2C%20making%20landfall%20near%20Acapulco.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-latin-america-67216467%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Israel%20Is%20Attacking%20South%20Gaza%20After%20Telling%20Civilians%20To%20Go%20There%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20told%20civilians%20in%20the%20northern%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20including%20residents%20of%20Gaza%20City%2C%20to%20move%20to%20the%20south%20of%20the%20enclave%2C%20saying%20it%20will%20be%20safer%20there%20as%20the%20military%20attacks%20Hamas%20following%20its%20Oct.%207%20cross-border%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Israeli%20warplanes%20have%20continued%20to%20hit%20sites%20in%20southern%20Gaza%2C%20spreading%20fear%20among%20the%20evacuees%20that%20they%20are%20just%20as%20vulnerable%20there%20as%20they%20were%20in%20their%20homes%20in%20the%20north.%20Here%20is%20an%20overview%20of%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHY%20IS%20ISRAEL%20STILL%20HITTING%20THE%20SOUTH%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20telling%20Gazans%20to%20head%20south%2C%20the%20Israeli%20military%20(IDF)%20has%20continued%20to%20pound%20targets%20across%20the%20area%2C%20killing%20an%20unknown%20number%20of%20civilians.%20In%20all%2C%20authorities%20in%20Gaza%20say%206%2C546%20Palestinians%20have%20died%20since%20Israeli%20strikes%20started%20on%20Oct.%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EResidents%20said%20the%20bombardment%20of%20the%20south%20intensified%20on%20Oct.%2025.%20One%20strike%20brought%20down%20several%20apartment%20buildings%20in%20Khan%20Younis%2C%20some%2010%20km%20(6%20miles)%20from%20the%20Egyptian%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20IDF%20has%20said%20that%20even%20if%20Hamas's%20main%20power%20centre%20is%20in%20Gaza%20City%2C%20it%20is%20nonetheless%20entrenched%20among%20the%20civilian%20population%20across%20the%20enclave.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWherever%20a%20Hamas%20target%20arises%2C%20the%20IDF%20will%20strike%20at%20it%20in%20order%20to%20thwart%20the%20terrorist%20capabilities%20of%20the%20group%2C%20while%20taking%20feasible%20precautions%20to%20mitigate%20the%20harm%20to%20uninvolved%20civilians%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20military%20said%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20reiterating%20previous%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20military%20has%20said%20the%20homes%20where%20operatives%20live%20are%20%26quot%3Blegitimate%20targets%26quot%3B%20even%20if%20civilians%20live%20alongside%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20so-called%20private%20home%20is%20not%20a%20private%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20Israeli%20air%20force%20officer%20told%20reporters%20in%20a%20recent%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHY%20DID%20ISRAEL%20ORDER%20THE%20EVACUATION%20SOUTH%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20said%20on%20Oct.%2012%20that%20nearly%20half%20of%20Gaza's%202.3%20million%20population%20should%20move%20to%20the%20southern%20half%20of%20Gaza%20within%2024%20hours.%20The%20military%20said%20the%20order%20was%20aimed%20at%20moving%20civilians%20away%20from%20%26quot%3BHamas%20terror%20targets%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20it%20believes%20are%20concentrated%20in%20the%20north.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMilitary%20spokesman%20Jonathan%20Conricus%20subsequently%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20preparing%20the%20area%20for%20significant%20military%20activity%20in%20Gaza%20City.%20That%20is%20the%20next%20stage.%20That's%20why%20we%20are%20asking%20civilians%20to%20go%20south%20of%20the%20Gaza%20River.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20massed%20troops%20on%20the%20border%20with%20Gaza%20and%20is%20widely%20expected%20to%20launch%20a%20land%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Oct.%2018%2C%20the%20military%20urged%20residents%20of%20Gaza%20to%20evacuate%20to%20what%20it%20called%20a%20humanitarian%20zone%20in%20Al%20Mawasi%2C%20on%20the%20coast%20of%20southern%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20renewed%20its%20warnings%20on%20Oct.%2022%2C%20saying%20that%20anyone%20staying%20in%20the%20north%20could%20be%20identified%20as%20sympathisers%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrorist%20organisation%26quot%3B%20if%20they%20did%20not%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHOW%20MANY%20PEOPLE%20HAVE%20MOVED%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20has%20urged%20Palestinians%20to%20ignore%20the%20Israeli%20warnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20it%20had%20attacked%20Hamas%20roadblocks%20that%20it%20believed%20were%20stopping%20people%20from%20evacuating.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20Hamas's%20attempts%20to%20stop%20an%20exodus%2C%20residents%20and%20international%20aid%20organisations%20say%20there%20has%20been%20a%20mass%20displacement%20of%20people%20away%20from%20the%20north%20and%20other%20areas%20of%20the%20enclave%20seen%20as%20especially%20vulnerable%20to%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20Office%20for%20the%20Coordination%20of%20Humanitarian%20Affairs%20(OCHA)%20estimated%20on%20Oct.%2024%20that%20more%20than%201.4%20million%20people%20are%20internally%20displaced%20(IDPs)%20within%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGaza's%20border%20crossings%20with%20both%20Egypt%20and%20Israel%20are%20closed%2C%20effectively%20trapping%20residents%20inside%20the%20enclave.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20HAS%20THE%20INTERNATIONAL%20COMMUNITY%20SAID%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUN%20Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20said%20giving%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20just%20hours%20to%20leave%20their%20homes%20was%20%26quot%3Bdangerous%20and%20deeply%20troubling%26quot%3B.%20Many%20Western%20governments%20have%20called%20for%20a%20pause%20in%20the%20fighting%20to%20open%20humanitarian%20corridors%20for%20the%20trapped%20civilians.%20Arab%20nations%20have%20called%20for%20Israel%20to%20stop%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698246180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fmqc2imm4_gaza-civilians-flee-afp_625x300_15_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-why-israel-is-attacking-south-gaza-after-telling-civilians-to-go-there-4513470%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel%20has%20told%20civilians%20in%20the%20northern%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20including%20residents%20of%20Gaza%20City%2C%20to%20move%20to%20the%20south%20of%20the%20enclave%2C%20saying%20it%20will%20be%20safer%20there%20as%20the%20military%20attacks%20Hamas%20following%20its%20Oct.%207%20cross-border%20assault.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-why-israel-is-attacking-south-gaza-after-telling-civilians-to-go-there-4513470%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-why-israel-is-attacking-south-gaza-after-telling-civilians-to-go-there-4513470%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22http