0a%20card-carrying%20member%20of%20the%20saffron%20party%20and%20recently%20said%20he%20does%20not%20want%20any%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fright-now-i-wont-seek-muslim-votes-himanta-biswa-sarma-exclusive-4290777%5C%22%3EMuslims%20to%20vote%20for%20him%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EZoramthanga%E2%80%99s%20recent%20statement%20may%20lead%20one%20to%20believe%20that%20the%2079-year-old%20veteran%20Mizo%20leader%20is%20the%20last%20of%20the%20old-school%20politicians%20from%20the%20Northeast%20who%20would%20not%20dither%20from%20questioning%20New%20Delhi%20if%20a%20local%20issue%20so%20warranted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EBirthday%20greetings%20to%20the%20Honourable%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20his%20exemplary%20leadership%20and%20supervision%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20position%20on%20every%20front%20has%20become%20much%20stronger%20than%20before%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FIndia%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23India%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20rising%20high%20in%20all%20aspects.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYour%20dedication%20in%20service%20to%20the%20nation%20is%20truly%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F6LoELGzSqQ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F6LoELGzSqQ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Zoramthanga%20(%40ZoramthangaCM)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZoramthangaCM%2Fstatus%2F1703404838187651372%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2017%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20his%20statement%2C%20as%20the%20state%20heads%20to%20an%20election%2C%20comes%20only%20after%20taking%20into%20consideration%20the%20multiple%20dynamics%20that%20he%20is%20juggling%20to%20be%20able%20to%20romp%20home%20to%20a%20victory%20for%20a%20second%20consecutive%20time.%20To%20my%20mind%2C%20there%20are%20at%20least%20five%20reasons%20why%20he%20has%20decided%20to%20snub%20Modi%20before%20the%20polls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChristian%20sentiments%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20there%20are%20other%20Christian-majority%20states%20in%20the%20northeast%2C%20the%20Church%20plays%20a%20prominent%20role%20in%20regulating%20the%20electoral%20process%20in%20Mizoram%20%E2%80%93%20albeit%20from%20the%20rear.%20No%20candidate%20can%20campaign%20door-to-door%20without%20a%20volunteer%20supplied%20by%20the%20Church-backed%20powerful%20civil%20society%20group%2C%20the%20Young%20Mizo%20Association%20(YMA).%20This%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20enticement%20is%20promised%20to%20the%20voters%20by%20any%20contender.%20No%20large%20poll-related%20spending%20is%20permitted%20to%20any%20party.%20Any%20defaulter%20would%20be%20named%20and%20shamed%20through%20the%20public%20address%20system%20that%20extends%20to%20every%20nook%20and%20cranny%20of%20Mizoram.%20Devout%20Mizos%20ardently%20follow%20those%20rules.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20the%20Christian-majority%20Kuki%20community%20was%20attacked%20in%20Imphal%20under%20the%20watch%20of%20a%20BJP%20chief%20minister%3B%20their%20homes%20and%20churches%20set%20on%20fire%2C%20has%20educed%20strong%20sentiments%20among%20the%20Mizos%2C%20a%20kindred%20community%20of%20the%20Kukis.%20Thousands%20have%20rushed%20into%20Mizoram%20for%20shelter%3B%20many%20are%20still%20staying%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuch%20attacks%20on%20Christians%20in%20a%20state%20ruled%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20whose%20Hindutva%20ideology%20makes%20no%20bones%20about%20opposition%20to%20religious%20minorities%2C%20have%20not%20gone%20unnoticed%20by%20the%20Church%20either.%20Several%20Church%20leaders%20have%20spoken%20about%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19190245%2FFN9Nlb3VgAEjWnO.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19190245%2FFN9Nlb3VgAEjWnO.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19190245%2FFN9Nlb3VgAEjWnO-300x150.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19190245%2FFN9Nlb3VgAEjWnO-1024x513.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19190245%2FFN9Nlb3VgAEjWnO-800x400.jpeg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-659017%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22601%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EManipur%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40NBirenSingh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you%20place%20Zoramthanga%E2%80%99s%20statement%20to%20the%20BBC%20in%20the%20light%20of%20this%20reality%2C%20it%20is%20only%20natural%20to%20conclude%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20is%20trying%20to%20address%20that%20latent%20anger%20in%20the%20deeply%20religious%20Mizos%20in%20this%20poll%20season.%20He%20hopes%20it%20will%20nudge%20them%20to%20press%20the%20Tiger%20head%2C%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20symbol%2C%20on%20the%20ballots%20on%20November%207.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMizo%20nationalism%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20MNF%20founding%20leader%20is%20also%20banking%20on%20the%20aid%20and%20assistance%20that%20his%20government%20has%20provided%20to%20those%20fleeing%20Manipur%20to%20help%20bind%20the%20Mizos%20in%20a%20strong%20sense%20of%20sub-nationalism%20under%20his%20leadership.%20The%20hapless%20Kukis%20arrived%20in%20Mizoram%20at%20a%20time%20when%20hundreds%20of%20Zo-Chin%20people%20from%20neighbouring%20Myanmar%20were%20also%20being%20offered%20food%20and%20shelter%20by%20the%20MNF%20and%20the%20YMA%2C%20in%20keeping%20with%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20Mizos.%20The%20Chins%20also%20belong%20to%20the%20larger%20Zo%20family%20of%20tribes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20Mizoram%20receiving%20so%20many%20refugees%20from%20its%20international%20and%20state%20borders%2C%20the%20long-forgotten%20demand%20for%20a%20larger%20Zo%20state%20comprising%20people%20of%20the%20same%20ancestry%20has%20once%20again%20risen%20its%20head.%20After%20the%20Manipur%20episode%2C%20Zoramthanga%20has%20particularly%20spoken%20about%20the%20need%20for%20%E2%80%98Zo%20unification%E2%80%99.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20not%20forget%2C%20he%20is%20one%20of%20the%20founding%20members%20of%20the%20MNF%2C%20which%20had%20once%20led%20a%20strong%20movement%20for%20Zo%20unification.%20In%202017%2C%20when%20the%20Modi%20government%20was%20initiating%20peace%20talks%20with%20the%20Kuki%20armed%20groups%20of%20Manipur%2C%20they%20preferred%20the%20Centre%20appoint%20Zoramthanga%20as%20the%20interlocutor.%20It%20didn%E2%80%99t%20materialise%2C%20but%20his%20leadership%20within%20the%20Zo%20people%20has%20not%20lost%20its%20significance.%20Kuki%20leaders%20from%20Manipur%20have%20already%20requested%20their%20Mizo%20brethren%20to%20re-elect%20Zoramthanga%E2%80%99s%20party%20in%20the%20coming%20polls.%20In%20such%20a%20sensitive%20situation%2C%20when%20Mizo%20voters%20are%20conscious%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20violence%20on%20the%20Kukis%20took%20place%20under%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20BJP%2C%20Zoramthanga%20would%20certainly%20not%20risk%20sharing%20the%20dais%20with%20the%20prime%20minister.%20Add%20to%20it%20the%20fact%20that%20Modi%20neither%20spoke%20about%20the%20violence%20nor%20visited%20the%20affected%20people%20%E2%80%93%20something%20which%20rankles%20both%20the%20Kuki%20and%20Meitei%20people%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20all%20the%20more%20necessary%20that%20Zoramthanga%20not%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20same%20frame%20as%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENDA%20ally%20%E2%80%93%20A%20baggage%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20Modi%20is%20set%20to%20campaign%20in%20Mizoram%20but%20does%20not%20want%20to%20visit%20Manipur%20only%20underlines%20the%20point%20that%20the%20BJP%20under%20him%20is%20quite%20ambitious%20about%20being%20part%20of%20the%20government%20in%20Mizoram.%20It%20is%20the%20only%20Northeastern%20state%20where%20the%20party%20is%20out%20of%20power.%20In%20Meghalaya%20and%20Nagaland%2C%20regional%20NDA%20partners%20have%20allowed%20it%20to%20become%20part%20of%20the%20governments%20though%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20have%20many%20MLAs.%20For%20the%20MNF%2C%20it%20has%20been%20difficult%20to%20enter%20into%20a%20poll%20alliance%20with%20the%20Hindutva-backed%20party%20in%20a%20Christian-majority%20state.%20In%20the%202018%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20facing%20huge%20anti-incumbency%2C%20had%20heightened%20its%20campaigning%20by%20particularly%20underlining%20that%20the%20MNF%20and%20BJP%20were%20allies%2C%20and%20therefore%20voting%20for%20one%20meant%20voting%20for%20the%20other.%20Zoramthanga%20did%20his%20best%20to%20convince%20the%20voters%20that%20if%20elected%2C%20he%20would%20never%20allow%20the%20BJP%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20his%20government.%20He%20stood%20by%20that%20word%20and%20kept%20the%20lone%20BJP%20MLA%20out%20of%20his%20regime%20despite%20substantial%20pressure%20from%20New%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20election%20too%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20upped%20its%20game%20by%20not%20only%20accusing%20the%20MNF%20government%20of%20corruption%20but%20also%20that%20the%20party%20is%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Felections%2Fmizoram-assembly%2Findia-bloc-represents-60-of-nation-rahul-gandhi%2Farticle67430034.ece%5C%22%3Eentry%20point%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20BJP-RSS.%20None%20other%20than%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20led%20that%20attack%20on%20Zoramthanga%E2%80%99s%20party%20during%20his%20recent%20visit%20to%20the%20state.%20In%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20Zoramthnaga%20would%20rather%20not%20share%20the%20stage%20with%20Modi.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18155141%2FRagul-in-Mizoram-IV.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18155141%2FRagul-in-Mizoram-IV.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18155141%2FRagul-in-Mizoram-IV-300x142.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18155141%2FRagul-in-Mizoram-IV-1024x486.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680646%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22569%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20in%20Aizawl%2C%20Mizoram%E2%80%99s%20capital.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2F%40RahulGandhi.%20October%2016%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ERise%20of%20ZPM%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20also%20accused%20the%20other%20regional%20party%2C%20the%20Zoram%20People%E2%80%99s%20Movement%20(ZPM)%2C%20of%20being%20close%20to%20the%20BJP-RSS.%20ZPM%20founder%20Lalduhoma%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Felections%2Flalduhoma-manipur-is-not-a-factor-in-mizoram-all-parties-here-on-same-page-on-issue-8998128%2F%5C%22%3Ewith%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20October%2025%2C%20denied%20the%20claim.%20But%20his%20words%20showed%20a%20whiff%20of%20Mizo%20sub-nationalism%3A%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20are%20not%20going%20to%20join%20any%20group%20at%20the%20national%20level%20because%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20have%20bosses%20in%20Delhi%20who%20will%20dictate%20us%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20ZPM%20%E2%80%9Cis%20a%20regional%20party%20with%20a%20national%20outlook%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20which%20reminded%20one%20of%20the%20Nagaland%20model%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20forged%20an%20alliance%20with%20a%20new%20regional%20party%2C%20the%20NDPP%2C%20when%20the%20old%20guard%20of%20the%20Naga%20People%E2%80%99s%20Front%20(NPF)%20refused%20to%20have%20any%20poll%20truck%20with%20it%20in%202017.%20Today%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20in%20government%20with%20the%20NDPP%2C%20which%20is%20also%20hinged%20on%20regionalism%20with%20a%20%E2%80%98national%20outlook%E2%80%99.%20The%20December%203%20results%20will%20decide%20whether%20Mizoram%20will%20see%20a%20repeat%20of%20the%20Nagaland%20model.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETill%20then%20though%2C%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20ZPM%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20the%20MNF%20is%20a%20headache%20for%20Zoramthanga.%20Considering%20his%20age%2C%20this%20is%20most%20likely%20to%20be%20his%20last%20election.%20He%20would%20rather%20not%20be%20remembered%20for%20hanging%20up%20his%20boots%20with%20a%20defeat%20for%20the%20MNF.%20If%20that%20calls%20for%20staying%20away%20from%20Modi%2C%20so%20be%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20entry%20into%20Mizo%20society%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20concerns%20of%20the%20MNF%2C%20though%2C%20is%20the%20rise%20of%20rebellion%20within%20the%20party%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20making%20good%20use%20of%20it%20to%20enamour%20the%20Mizo%20society.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20run-up%20to%20these%20polls%2C%20MNF%20lost%20two%20of%20its%20senior%20MLAs%2C%20one%20of%20them%20the%20speaker%2C%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Until%20the%202018%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20could%20find%20winnable%20candidates%20only%20within%20the%20Chakma%20community.%20Not%20anymore.%20If%20these%20candidates%20can%20pull%20off%20a%20win%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20likely%20put%20ample%20pressure%20on%20the%20winning%20party%20(MNF%20or%20ZPM)%20to%20accommodate%20it%20in%20the%20next%20government.%20No%20way%20would%20Zoramthanga%20then%20want%20voters%20to%20see%20it%20as%20a%20friendly%20contest%20by%20posing%20next%20to%20Modi%20in%20an%20election%20rally%20and%20thereby%20help%20the%20rebels%20reap%20any%20electoral%20benefits.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698244853000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25200711%2FW8HqhiLc_400x400.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffive-reasons-mizoram-cm-zoramthanga-shun-modi-election%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Wire%20explains%20the%20compulsions%20that%20forced%20the%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20chief%20to%20make%20such%20a%20categorical%20statement%20against%20the%20prime%20minister%20despite%20his%20party%20being%20part%20of%20the%20NDA.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffive-reasons-mizoram-cm-zoramthanga-shun-modi-election%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20approves%20Rs%2022%2C303%20cr%20subsidy%20on%20P%26amp%3BK%20fertilizers%20for%20rabi%20season%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698244749000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2021-11%2F29%2Ffull%2F1638154784-1743.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fcentre-approves-rs-22-303-cr-subsidy-on-p-k-fertilizers-for-rabi-season-123102501031_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20FY24%20Budget%20had%20estimated%20the%20subsidy%20expenditure%20on%20non-urea%20fertilisers%20at%20Rs%2044%2C000%20crore%20for%20the%202023-24%20financial%20year%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fcentre-approves-rs-22-303-cr-subsidy-on-p-k-fertilizers-for-rabi-season-123102501031_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fcentre-approves-rs-22-303-cr-subsidy-on-p-k-fertilizers-for-rabi-season-123102501031_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fcentre-approves-rs-22-303-cr-subsidy-on-p-k-fertilizers-for-rabi-season-123102501031_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Woman%20With%20Rare%20Heart%20Condition%20Says%20%26quot%3BI%20Run%20On%20Batteries%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2030-year-old%20woman%20from%20Massachusetts%2C%20Sofia%20Hart%2C%20is%20living%20with%20a%20rare%20genetic%20heart%20condition%20that%20has%20left%20her%20without%20a%20pulse%2C%20and%20she%20describes%20herself%20as%20%26quot%3Brunning%20on%20batteries.%26quot%3B%20She%20has%20been%20diagnosed%20with%20irreversible%20dilated%20cardiomyopathy%2C%20a%20heart%20muscle%20disorder%20that%20affects%20one%20of%20the%20ventricles%2C%20potentially%20leading%20to%20heart%20failure.%20Sofia%20relies%20on%20a%20life-saving%20medical%20device%20called%20the%20LVAD%20(Left%20Ventricular%20Assist%20Device)%20to%20ensure%20her%20heart%20keeps%20beating%20as%20she%20awaits%20a%20heart%20transplant.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20left%20ventricular%20assist%20device%20(LVAD)%20aids%20in%20maintaining%20blood%20circulation%20throughout%20the%20body%20by%20mechanically%20assisting%20the%20left%20side%20of%20the%20heart%20in%20pumping.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Fwoman-has-no-pulse-runs-on-batteries-sofia-hart-tiktok-lvad-exclusive-8367390%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20People%20magazine%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ms%20Hart%20discovered%20she%20had%20the%20condition%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202022%20while%20working%20at%20a%20horse%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20%3Cem%3EPeople%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20'I%20started%20getting%20really%20achy%20and%20so%20fatigued.%20It's%20like%20a%20fatigue%20that%20you%20can't%20really%20describe.%20I%20wasn't%20tired%20in%20my%20brain%2C%20but%20my%20body%20was%20so%20tired.'%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Hart's%20twin%20sister%20Olivia%20was%20born%20with%20the%20same%20rare%20genetic%20mutation%2C%20it%20wasn't%20discovered%20until%20Sofia%20also%20became%20ill.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20sister%20had%20also%20suffered%20heart%20disease%20seven%20years%20prior%2C%20but%20genetics%20wasn't%20among%20the%20factors%20considered%20until%20both%20of%20them%20were%20confirmed%20to%20suffer%20heart%20failure%20at%20a%20young%20age.%20Similarly%2C%20Olivia%20also%20had%20to%20get%20an%20LVAD%20device%20until%20her%20transplant%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Sofia%20has%20to%20do%20the%20same%20and%20live%20with%20the%20device%20until%20she%20gets%20a%20transplant.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20doing%20the%20work-up%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20tells%20%3Cem%3EPeople%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20guilty%20having%20the%20option%20of%20finding%20my%20footing%20before%20jumping%20into%20a%20transplant.%20I%20came%20out%20of%20the%20gates%20hot%20and%20then%20realised%2C%20well%2C%20the%20device%20is%20doing%20well%2C%20I'm%20doing%20well%20on%20the%20device%2C%20transplant%20is%20such%20a%20huge%2C%20huge%2C%20huge%20deal%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20life%2C%20transplant%2C%20live%20with%20%26quot%3BJanis%26quot%3B-the%20name%20I%20gave%20my%20LVAD-accept%20all%20that's%20changed%2C%20and%20now%20I'm%20ready%20to%20go%20to%20transplant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698244620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fa6gsel38_sofia-hart-has-irreversible-dilated-cardi