overnment%20that%20gives%20reservations%20to%20these%20communities%2C%20Ms%20Sule%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20demanding%20that%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20hold%20a%20special%20assembly%20session%20on%20reservations%20for%20the%20Dhangar%2C%20Maratha%2C%20Lingayat%20and%20Muslim%20communities.%20NCP%20will%20support%20any%20government%20that%20gives%20reservations%20to%20these%20communities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Supriya%20Sule%20said%20on%20Sunday%20that%20there%20is%20only%20one%20Shiv%20Sena%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20which%20was%20formed%20by%20the%20late%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20responding%20to%20Union%20Minister%20Nitin%20Gadkari's%20statement%20about%20the%20real%20Shiv%20Sena%20during%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr%20Gadkari%20is%20the%20only%20person%20in%20the%20BJP%20who%20speaks%20the%20truth%3B%20for%20me%2C%20there%20is%20only%20one%20Shivsena%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20which%20was%20formed%20by%20the%20late%20Balasaheba%20Thackeray%2C%20and%20he%20handed%20over%20the%20responsibility%20to%20Uddhav%20while%20he%20was%20alive.%20There%20are%20duplicate%20things%20currently%2C%20but%20people%20know%20the%20exact%20difference%20between%20gold%20and%20bronze%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20reporters%20in%20Pune%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20chief%20Sharad%20Pawar%20flagged%20off%20the%20'Yuva%20Sangharsh%20Yatra'%20in%20Pune%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20said%20that%20youth%20in%20the%20state%20cannot%20be%20ignored%20if%20those%20in%20the%20government%20want%20to%20remain%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20said%2C%26quot%3B%20'Yuva%20Sangharsh%20Yatra'%2C%20started%20by%20Rohit%20Pawar%2C%20will%20give%20faith%20and%20strength%20to%20all%20the%20youth%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20starting%20from%20Pune%20today.%20Guided%20all%20the%20young%20people%20present%20on%20this%20occasion.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20small%20Yatra.%20It%20will%20last%20for%2045%20days%20in%20total.%20This%20is%20for%20the%20new%20generation.%20This%20is%20a%20confidence%20booster%20for%20the%20new%20generation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20that%20%26quot%3Byouth%20cannot%20be%20ignored%20in%20the%20state%26quot%3B%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20anyone%20takes%20a%20stand%20of%20neglecting%20the%20youth%2C%20then%20the%20government%20will%20have%20to%20pay%20a%20heavy%20price%20and%20hence%20this%20Yatra%20is%20very%20important.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698243900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fk6psitbo_supriya-sule_625x300_05_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsharad-pawar-daughter-supriya-sule-on-maratha-reservation-says-nitin-gadkari-only-person-in-bjp-who-speaks-truth-4513011%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20MP%20(Sharad%20Pawar%20faction)%20Supriya%20Sule%20on%20Wednesday%20claimed%20that%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bpolicy%20paralysis%20in%20Maharashtra%20government%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20issue%20of%20Maratha%20reservation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsharad-pawar-daughter-supriya-sule-on-maratha-reservation-says-nitin-gadkari-only-person-in-bjp-who-speaks-truth-4513011%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsharad-pawar-daughter-supriya-sule-on-maratha-reservation-says-nitin-gadkari-only-person-in-bjp-who-speaks-truth-4513011%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsharad-pawar-daughter-supriya-sule-on-maratha-reservation-says-nitin-gadkari-only-person-in-bjp-who-sp