C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D332890%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20astrophotography%20to%20capturing%20the%20moods%20of%20the%20ocean%2C%20these%20five%20photographers%20prove%20that%20each%20picture%20opens%20the%20doors%20to%20a%20whole%20new%20world.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20a%20look%20at%20their%20work.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332890%2Findian-photographers-pictures-military-navy-wildlife-oceans-astronomy%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani%20Auditor%20EY%20Faces%20Inquiry%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20Accounting%20Regulator%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25192401%2FSecretary_Kerry_greets_Executive_Chairman_Adani_before_meeting_with_Indian_CEOs_amid_Vibrant_Gujarat_Summit.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22paragraph-0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20accounting%20regulator%2C%20the%20National%20Financial%20Reporting%20Authority%20(NFRA)%2C%20has%20initiated%20an%20inquiry%20against%20one%20of%20EY%E2%80%99s%20member%20firms%20in%20the%20country%2C%20S.R.%20Batliboi%2C%20which%20audits%20certain%20Adani%20Group%20companies%2C%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-10-25%2Fadani-auditor-ey-faces-inquiry-by-india-s-accounting-regulator%23xj4y7vzkg%5C%22%3Ereported%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20citing%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%2C%20on%20Wednesday%20(October%2025).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22paragraph-0%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20NFRA%E2%80%99s%20inquiry%20began%20in%20recent%20weeks.%20The%20National%20Financial%20Reporting%20Authority%20has%20requested%20documents%20and%20communications%20related%20to%20the%20audits%20of%20Adani-controlled%20companies%20dating%20back%20to%202014%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ES.R.%20Batliboi%20currently%20audits%20five%20of%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20listed%20firms%20%E2%80%93%20Adani%20Power%2C%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%2C%20Adani%20Wilmar%2C%20and%20recently%20acquired%20cement%20companies%20ACC%20and%20Ambuja%20Cements.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%2C%20however%2C%20remains%20unclear%20how%20long%20the%20NFRA%E2%80%99s%20inquiry%20could%20take%20or%20what%20repercussions%2C%20if%20any%2C%20could%20be%20faced%20by%20the%20auditor%20or%20the%20audited%2C%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBloomberg%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20sought%20comments%20from%20the%20auditor%20and%20the%20Adani%20Group.%20Both%20parties%20did%20not%20respond.%20A%20representative%20for%20EY%20and%20S.R.%20Batliboi%20also%20declined%20to%20comment%2C%20as%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22paragraph-3%5C%22%3EIn%20August%2C%20Deloitte%2C%20Haskins%20%26amp%3B%20Sells%20LLP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fdeloitte-resigns-as-the-statutory-auditors-of-adani-ports-and-special-economic-zone%5C%22%3Ehad%20resigned%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20statutory%20auditors%20of%20Adani%20Ports%20and%20Special%20Economic%20Zone%20(APSEZ).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22paragraph-3%5C%22%3EIn%20May%2C%20the%20audit%20firm%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fdeloitte-raises-related-party-concerns-over-adani-ports-deals-with-3-entities%5C%22%3Ehad%20flagged%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0some%20transactions%20by%20Adani%20Group%2C%20citing%20allegations%20from%20US-based%20short%20seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%E2%80%99s%20report%20that%20wiped%20off%20half%20of%20the%20market%20value%20of%20the%20ports-to-power%20conglomerate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22paragraph-3%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20same%20month%2C%20Ahme%C2%ADdabad-based%20chartered%20accountancy%20firm%20Shah%20Dhandharia%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20named%20in%20Hindenburg%20Research%E2%80%99s%20report%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fshah-dhandharia-named-in-hindenburg-report-resigns-as-adani-total-gass-statutory-auditor%5C%22%3Ehad%20resigned%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20statutory%20auditor%20of%20Adani%20Total%20Gas.%20It%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-row-auditor-named-in-hindenburg-report-resigns-cites-preoccupation%2Fcid%2F1933967%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20it%20had%20decided%20to%20resign%20%E2%80%9Cdue%20to%20increased%20professional%20preoccupation%20in%20other%20assignments%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202022%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EMorning%20Context%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthemorningcontext.com%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-groups-auditing-practices-need-looking-into%5C%22%3Ehad%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20two%20accountancy%20firms%20%E2%80%93%20Shah%20Dhandharia%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20and%20Dharmesh%20Parikh%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20%E2%80%93%20that%20audit%20most%20of%20Adani%20Group%20companies%20have%20links%20to%20each%20other%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20raise%20concerns%20over%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20corporate%20governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20said%20that%20Adani%20Group%20paid%20them%20a%20little%20over%20Rs%207%20crore%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20Rs%2084%20crore%20paid%20by%20Mukesh%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20Reliance%20Industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUS-based%20short%20seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%2C%20in%20its%20January%2024%20report%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhindenburgresearch.com%2Fadani%2F%5C%22%3Ehad%20also%20raised%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20issue%20of%20the%20size%20and%20capability%20of%20the%20firms%20auditing%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698241917000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25192401%2FSecretary_Kerry_greets_Executive_Chairman_Adani_before_meeting_with_Indian_CEOs_amid_Vibrant_Gujarat_Summit.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-auditor-ey-faces-inquiry-by-indias-accounting-regulator-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20National%20Financial%20Reporting%20Authority%20has%20requested%20documents%20and%20communications%20related%20to%20the%20audits%20of%20Adani-controlled%20companies%20dating%20back%20to%202014%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-auditor-ey-faces-inquiry-by-indias-accounting-regulator-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Tackling%20India's%20Stray%20Dog%20Menace%20-%20All%20Bark%2C%20No%20Bite%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGujarat%20businessman%20Parag%20Desai's%20death%20in%20Ahmedabad%20recently%20has%20reignited%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20stray%20dog%20menace%20in%20India.%20Mr%20Desai%20fell%20while%20being%20chased%20by%20street%20dogs%20during%20his%20morning%20walk.%20He%20suffered%20head%20injuries%20and%20died%20of%20a%20brain%20haemorrhage%20days%20later.%20Almost%20every%20week%2C%20dog%20attack%20deaths%20are%20reported%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20each%20more%20gruesome%20than%20the%20previous.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20statistics%20of%20such%20deaths%20are%20horrific%20and%20speak%20for%20themselves.%20India%20reported%20nearly%2016%20million%20cases%20of%20stray%20dog%20bites%20between%202019%20and%202022%20(parliament%20data%20till%20November%202022)%2C%20an%20average%20of%20over%2010%2C000%20cases%20daily.%20The%20National%20Rabies%20Control%20Programme%20reported%206%2C644%20clinically%20suspected%20cases%20and%20deaths%20of%20human%20rabies%20between%202012%20and%202022%20in%20India.%20Between%20January%20and%20October%202022%2C%20Kerala%20and%20Punjab%20reported%20over%2010%2C000%20cases%20each%2C%20while%201%2C000-10%2C000%20cases%20were%20reported%20from%20Maharashtra%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20Kashmir.%20About%20200%20dog%20bites%20were%20reported%20every%20day%20from%20Ahmedabad%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20figures%20speak%20poorly%20of%20India%20as%20it%20strives%20to%20be%20a%20developed%20nation.%20When%20developed%20countries%20have%20been%20able%20to%20control%20the%20stray%20menace%2C%20what%20stops%20us%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20it%20is%20illegal%20to%20remove%20stray%20dogs%20from%20the%20streets%20and%20they%20cannot%20be%20driven%20away%20either.%20Stray%20dogs%20continue%20to%20remain%20on%20the%20roads%20until%20they%20are%20adopted%2C%20which%20is%20rare.%20This%20creates%20a%20perfect%20environment%20for%20the%20problem%20to%20grow%20and%20flourish.%20The%20Animal%20Birth%20Control%20Program%202001%2C%20introduced%20by%20the%20government%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20controlling%20stray%20dogs%20through%20sterilisation%20and%20vaccination%2C%20has%20failed%20because%20of%20poor%20implementation.%20Local%20municipal%20corporations%20and%20NGOs%20tasked%20with%20carrying%20out%20sterilisations%20cite%20lack%20of%20funds%20and%20resources%2C%20corruption%2C%20and%20lack%20of%20coordination%20between%20government%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20municipalities%20under%20the%20Animal%20Birth%20Control%20Rules%2C%202023%2C%20to%20run%20an%20effective%20dog%20sterilisation%20programme.%20Sterilisations%20are%20simple%20surgeries%20that%20prevent%20births.%20Getting%20dogs%20sterilised%20has%20been%20a%20requirement%20for%2022%20years%2C%20previously%20mandated%20under%20the%20Animal%20Birth%20Control%20(Dog)%20Rules%2C%202001%2C%20which%20has%20now%20been%20replaced%20by%20Animal%20Birth%20Control%20Rules%2C%202023.%20If%20all%20municipalities%20had%20taken%20this%20lawful%20duty%20seriously%2C%20there%20would%20hardly%20be%20any%20dogs%20on%20the%20road%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Meet%20Ashar%2C%20Cruelty%20Case%20Division%20Legal%20Advisor%20and%20Manager%2C%20PETA%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20a%20love-hate%20relationship%20with%20stray%20dogs.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20countless%20people%20feed%20strays%20as%20an%20act%20of%20kindness%2C%20and%20on%20the%20other%2C%20there%20is%20a%20rising%20number%20of%20human%20lives%20lost%20to%20stray%20dog%20bites.%20Disposal%20of%20waste%20in%20the%20open%20attracts%20stray%20dogs%20at%20times%2C%20leaving%20them%20hungry%20-%20or%20only%20partly%20sated%20-%20and%20aggressive.%20The%20absence%20of%20waste%20management%20to%20address%20open%20litter%20on%20roads%20is%20another%20contributor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20pandemic%20appears%20to%20have%20impacted%20the%20stray%20population%20too%2C%20turning%20them%20more%20feral%20than%20before.%20Animal%20experts%20say%20that%20post-pandemic%2C%20stray%20dogs%20are%20seen%20to%20have%20become%20more%20aggressive%20due%20to%20food%20shortages%2C%20the%20abandonment%20of%20pets%2C%20and%20a%20decrease%20in%20human-dog%20interactions.%20Dogs%20being%20fed%20in%20the%20same%20area%20makes%20them%20insecure%20about%20their%20space%20and%20intensely%20territorial.%20It%20becomes%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20dog%20feeder%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20stray%20is%20vaccinated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20horrifying%20videos%20of%20dog%20bite%20incidents%20that%20go%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20include%20calls%20for%20strong%20action%20to%20curb%20the%20menace.%20Reports%20have%20often%20surfaced%20of%20the%20face-off%20between%20animal%20lovers%20and%20those%20opposing%20their%20activities%20in%20public%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20tweet%20by%20senior%20IPS%20officer%20Arun%20Bothra%20after%20the%20Parag%20Desai%20incident%20drew%20support%20as%20well%20as%20outrage.%20%26quot%3BCarry%20a%20stick%20to%20keep%20safe%20from%20stray%20dogs%20on%20morning%20walks.%20If%20there%20are%20dog%20lover%20activists%20in%20your%20area%2C%20carry%20a%20bigger%20stick%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFacing%20a%20backlash%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20in%20any%20way%20advocating%20violence%2C%20my%20only%20concern%20is%20no%20one%20should%20fall%20prey%20to%20dog%20bites.%20When%20one%20goes%20out%20for%20a%20walk%2C%20one%20is%20compelled%20to%20carry%20the%20stick%20for%20self-defence.%20Nobody%20goes%20out%20for%20a%20walk%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20hurting%20the%20dog.%20Dog%20lover-activists%20must%20understand%20and%20acknowledge%20that%20stray%20dogs%20are%20a%20problem%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20accounts%20for%2036%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20world's%20rabies%20deaths%2C%20according%20to%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%20(WHO).%20%26quot%3BMost%20children%20and%20elderly%20people%20bitten%20by%20strays%20are%20from%20the%20lower%20income%20group%20-%20they%20cannot%20afford%20expensive%20rabies%20vaccines%20and%20eventually%20die.%20Isn't%20that%20sad%3F%20So%20many%20people%20have%20liked%20the%20tweet%2C%20it%20shows%20they%20too%20are%20facing%20the%20stray%20menace%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bothra%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20talked%20about%20a%20durable%20and%20humane%20solution%20to%20human-stray%20dog%20conflicts%20in%20the%20context%20of%20Kerala.%20In%20response%20to%20the%20Kerala%20government's%20proposal%20to%20cull%20%26quot%3Baggressive%20and%20rabid%26quot%3B%20dogs%2C%20animal%20activists%20argued%20that%20addressing%20the%20root%20causes%20of%20the%20problem%20is%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSterilisation%20and%20supporting%20dog%20feeders%20who%20turn%20dogs%20trusting%20and%20friendly%20are%20the%20only%20humane%2C%20legal%20and%20effective%20options%20to%20stem%20India's%20stray%20animal%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20explained%20Mr%20Ashar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20one%20estimate%2C%20he%20said%2C%20one%20unaltered%20dog%20and%20her%20offspring%20can%20produce%2067%2C000%20puppies%20in%20six%20years.%20%26quot%3BA%20robust%20and%20effective%20sterilisation%20programme%20can%20help%20prevent%20this%20as%20stray%20dogs%20are%20surgically%20neutered%20and%20then%20released%20back%20in%20the%20same%20area%20from%20which%20they%20were%20picked%20up%2C%20as%20dogs%20are%20territorial%20in%20nature.%20Sterilised%20dogs%20are%20also%20vaccinated%20against%20rabies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20insiders%20demur.%20%26quot%3BStray%20dogs%20are%20released%20on%20the%20roads%20without%20vaccination.%20Their%20ears%20are%20pierced%20(a%20permanent%20identification%20mark%20showing%20that%20a%20stray%20has%20been%20sterilised)%20without%20the%20process%20being%20actually%20carried%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20in%20many%20other%20areas%20of%20public%20service%2C%20in%20animal%20control%20too%2C%20the%20problem%20is%20not%20the%20lack%20of%20policies%20but%20the%20inefficient%20execution%20of%20sterilisation%20programmes%20that%20have%20resulted%20in%20the%20failure%20to%20control%20the%20stray%20dog%20boom%20in%20our%20country.%20With%20each%20fatal%20dog%20bite%2C%20there%20is%20an%20uproar%20but%20those%20responsible%20for%20managing%20the%20menace%20always%20fail%20to%20take%20ownership.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698241860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F7fnj00o_dog-generic_625x300_31_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ftackling-indias-stray-dog-menace-all-bark-no-bite-4513275%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gujarat%20businessman%20Parag%20Desai's%20death%20in%20Ahmedabad%20recently%20has%20reignited%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20stray%20dog%20menace%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ftackling-indias-stray-dog-menace-all-bark-no-bite-4513275%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hostage%20negotiations%20could%20be%20jeopardised%20by%20Gaza%20ground%20offensive%2C%20mediators%20warn%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698241800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2Fskynews-israel-lebanon-soldier_6334937.jpg%3F20231025105642%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fnegotiations-to-free-more-gaza-hostages-could-be-jeopardised-by-israeli-ground-attack-qatari-mediators-warn-12992392%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Negotiations%20to%20release%20more%20Hamas%20hostages%20from%20Gaza%20are%20ongoing%20but%20could%20be%20jeopardised%20by%20an%20Israeli%20ground%20offensive%2C%20Qatari%20mediators%20have%20warned.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fnegotiations-to-free-more-gaza-hostages-could-be-jeopardised-by-israeli-ground-attack-qatari-mediators-warn-12992392%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fnegotiations-to-free-more-gaza-hostages-could-be-jeopardised-by-israeli-ground-attack-qatari-mediators-warn-12992392%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fnegotiations-to-free-more-gaza-hostages-could-be-jeopardised-by-israeli-ground-attack-qatari-mediators-warn-12992392%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dunki%20teaser%20to%20be%20attached%20to%20Tiger%203%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698241713000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104703367%2Cimgsize-53378.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khans-dunki-teaser-to-be-attached-to-salman-khans-tiger-3%2Farticleshow%2F104703407.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104703407.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EShah%20Rukh%20Khan%20plans%20to%20attach%20the%20%26quot%3BDunki%26quot%3B%20teaser%20to%20Salman%20Khan's%20%26quot%3BTiger%203%2C%26quot%3B%20reciprocating%20their%20friendship.%20The%20move%20aims%20to%20capture%20a%20broad%20audience%20for%20the%20highly%20anticipated%20%26quot%3BDunki.%26quot%3B%20SRK's%20cameo%20in%20%26quot%3BTiger%203%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20teaser%20itself%20offer%20fans%20a%20double%20bonanza.%20This%20strategic%20decision%20reinforces%20SRK's%20potential%20to%20have%20a%20third%20consecutive%20blockbuster%20in%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khans-dunki-teaser-to-be-attached-to-salman-khans-tiger-3%2Farticleshow%2F104703407.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel-Palestine%20Conflict%3A%20Why%20Has%20India%20Forsaken%20Its%20Role%20as%20a%20Voice%20of%20Moderation%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25174409%2Fimage-1432.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20sad%20to%20see%20how%20Indians%20have%20changed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Palestinian%20author%20Susan%20Abulhawa%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIndiaToday%2Fstatus%2F1713952486036590899%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20Rajdeep%20Sardesai.%20She%20said%20that%20she%20was%20surprised%20that%20Indians%2C%20who%20have%20experienced%20the%20cruelty%20of%20colonialism%2C%20fail%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%2C%20which%20has%20faced%20the%20brunt%20of%20settler%20colonialism%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20Israel.%20How%20can%20Indians%20wish%20for%20the%20extermination%20of%20the%20occupied%20people%20of%20Gaza%20and%20wish%20victory%20for%20the%20occupier%20Israel%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20reasons%20for%20the%20change%20that%20India%20has%20gone%20through%20in%20the%20recent%20past.%20One%20reason%20for%20this%20change%20is%20the%20fading%20memory%20of%20English%20colonialism%2C%20with%20the%20Mughals%2FMuslims%20being%20increasingly%20seen%20as%20the%20real%20colonisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20world%2C%20yet%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20the%20change%20in%20the%20imagination%20of%20the%20Hindu%20majority%2C%20was%20surprised%20to%20see%20massive%20support%20for%20the%20Israeli%20war%20against%20the%20Palestinians%20coming%20from%20India.%20One%20person%20noted%20that%20it%20was%20amusing%20to%20see%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20social%20media%20posts%20calling%20for%20an%20end%20to%20the%20war%20in%20Hebrew%20and%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20posts%20calling%20for%20the%20annihilation%20of%20Gaza%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNu8B5Jjy1is%5C%22%3Ein%20Hindi%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20may%20have%20been%20exaggerating%2C%20but%20it%20is%20true%20that%20there%20was%20an%20obscene%20glee%20in%20the%20Indian%20media%20after%20Israel%20started%20to%20bomb%20Gaza%20in%20retaliation%20for%20the%20surprise%20Hamas%20attack%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2Fpalestinian-deaths-toll-war-gaza-israel-hamas%2Farticle67423083.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520current%2520war%2520erupted%2520a%2CThe%2520overwhelming%2520majority%2520were%2520civilians.%5C%22%3Ekilled%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20than%201%2C300%20Israelis%2C%20most%20of%20them%20civilians%2C%20and%20took%20more%20than%20200%20Israelis%20as%20hostages%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fhostage-families-face-appalling-dilemma-gaza-invasion-looms-2023-10-23%2F%5C%22%3Eto%20be%20exchanged%20with%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20than%205%2C000%20Palestinians%2C%20including%20children%20and%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20has%20to%20be%20fair%20to%20the%20Indian%20media.%20It%20was%20after%20all%20not%20very%20different%20from%20its%20Western%20counterpart%2C%20which%20was%20demonstratively%20partisan%20towards%20Israel.%20A%20majority%20of%20TV%20channels%20and%20newspapers%20actively%20decontextualised%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20and%20also%20failed%20to%20see%20and%20point%20out%20the%20visible%20disproportionality%20in%20the%20Israeli%20%E2%80%98response%E2%80%99.%20The%20killing%20of%20Israeli%20children%20and%20women%20outraged%20them.%20But%20the%20killing%20of%20Gazan%20babies%20by%20the%20indiscriminate%20bombing%20was%20because%20of%20Hamas%20embedding%20themselves%20within%20the%20civilian%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20on%20civilians%20was%20justified%20by%20suggesting%20that%20without%20their%20support%2C%20Hamas%20would%20not%20thrive.%20If%20they%20were%20not%20revolting%20against%20Hamas%2C%20they%20were%20complicit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Western%20media%20and%20political%20leadership%20kept%20calling%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20%E2%80%98unprovoked%E2%80%99%2C%20totally%20neglecting%20the%20underlying%20context%20%E2%80%93%20which%20includes%20the%20daily%20violence%20against%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20not%20only%20by%20the%20Israel%20Defence%20Forces%20(IDF)%20but%20also%20by%20settlers%20who%20are%20given%20arms%20and%20cover%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fisrael-news%2F2019-03-12%2Fty-article%2F.premium%2Fhow-palestinian-land-goes-from-the-army-to-the-settlers%2F0000017f-e3ae-d804-ad7f-f3fe6a2f0000%5C%22%3EIsraeli%20state%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2021%2F7%2F8%2Fhow-israel-backs-settlers-to-confiscate-palestinian-lands%5C%22%3Eloot%20and%20steal%20Palestinian%20land%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20houses%20and%20even%20kill.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECalling%20out%20this%20dishonesty%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.democracynow.org%2F2023%2F10%2F19%2Famira_hass_on_gaza_humanitarian_crisis%5C%22%3EAmira%20Hass%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20veteran%20Israeli-Jewish%20journalist%2C%20plainly%20said%20that%20history%20did%20not%20begin%20on%20October%207%2C%202023.%20The%20Hamas%20attack%2C%20she%20said%2C%20may%20not%20have%20happened%20if%20Israel%20had%20not%20committed%20unspeakable%20atrocities%20on%20the%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%2C%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20even%20Jerusalem.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F15164743%2Ftaylor-brandon-Y8r0RTNrIWM-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F15164743%2Ftaylor-brandon-Y8r0RTNrIWM-unsplash.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F15164743%2Ftaylor-brandon-Y8r0RTNrIWM-unsplash-300x159.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F15164743%2Ftaylor-brandon-Y8r0RTNrIWM-unsplash-1024x541.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-640667%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22634%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAn%20Israeli%20flag.%20Representative%20image.%20Photo%3A%20Taylor%20Brandon%2FUnsplash%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Indian%20media%20went%20berserk%2C%20asking%20for%20the%20total%20destruction%20of%20and%20predicting%20the%20end%20of%20Gaza.%20It%20seems%20to%20have%20taken%20a%20cue%20from%20the%20first%20reaction%20of%20its%20chief%20editor%2C%20who%20also%20happens%20to%20be%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20India.%20Narendra%20Modi%20took%20to%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20immediately%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CDeeply%20shocked%20by%20the%20news%20of%20terrorist%20attacks%20in%20Israel.%20Our%20thoughts%20and%20prayers%20are%20with%20the%20innocent%20victims%20and%20their%20families.%20We%20stand%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Israel%20at%20this%20difficult%20hour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20big%20media%20tried%20to%20portray%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fstand-in-solidarity-with-israel-at-this-difficult-hour-pm-modi%2Farticleshow%2F104241034.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmodi-reiterates-solidarity-phone-call-netanyahu-israel-hamas%5C%22%3EModi%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98s%20entry%20into%20the%20war%20against%20%E2%80%98terror%E2%80%99%2C%20which%2C%20according%20to%20it%2C%20has%20driven%20fear%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20others%20noted%20that%20India%20had%20associated%20its%20reputation%20with%20Israel%20and%20forsaken%20its%20role%20as%20a%20voice%20of%20moderation%2C%20which%20it%20has%20performed%20historically%20since%20independence.%20While%20expressing%20shock%20at%20the%20Hamas%20attack%2C%20India%20could%20have%20asked%20for%20restraint%2C%20by%20calling%20upon%20Israel%20not%20to%20target%20the%20civilian%20population%20of%20Gaza.%20Only%20five%20days%20later%2C%20it%20tried%20to%20correct%20its%20official%20position%20when%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Flatest%2Fworld%2Fstory%2Findia-supports-establishment-of-independent-state-of-palestine-mea-401804-2023-10-12%5C%22%3Ereiterated%20its%20stand%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20sovereign%20Palestine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20after%2018%20days%20of%20the%20Israeli%20bombing%20of%20Gaza%2C%20India%20has%20not%20called%20for%20a%20ceasefire.%20It%20has%20not%20called%20upon%20the%20international%20community%20to%20mediate.%20That%20indicates%20that%20it%20is%20allowing%20Israel%20to%20continue%20its%20genocidal%20attack%20on%20the%20civilian%20population%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisraels-war-on-palestinians-language-in-the-service-of-the-unspeakable%5C%22%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20War%20on%20Palestinians%3A%20Language%20in%20the%20Service%20of%20the%20Unspeakable%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20election%20agenda%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20journalist%20friend%20of%20mine%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Chandigarh%2C%20told%20me%20he%20is%20worried%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20Israeli%20%E2%80%98war%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20state%20elections%20to%20be%20held%20next%20month.%20His%20worry%20is%20not%20misplaced.%20If%20you%20follow%20the%20big%20media%2C%20which%20acts%20like%20a%20mouthpiece%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP%2C%20you%20can%20see%20that%20the%20trope%20of%20terror%20is%20being%20used%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhow-pro-bjp-whatsapp-facebook-groups-are-using-the-israel-hamas-war-to-stoke-islamophobia%5C%22%3Evilify%20Muslims%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20is%20suggested%20that%20Islamic%20countries%20should%20accommodate%20Palestinians%20and%20make%20Gaza%20available%20to%20Israel.%20This%20is%20what%20they%20have%20been%20wishing%20for%20Indian%20Muslims%3A%20to%20be%20packed%20off%20to%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20hard%20to%20ascertain%20that%20the%20conflict%20in%20West%20Asia%20would%20be%20used%20%E2%80%93%20is%20already%20being%20used%20%E2%80%93%20to%20demonise%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20propaganda%20cell%20is%20working%20overtime%20to%20tell%20its%20constituents%20that%20Palestinian%20%E2%80%98terror%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20result%20of%20the%20policies%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi%20or%20the%20Congress%20party.%20The%20Congress%20party%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fisrael-hamas-war-gaza-terrorist-attack-p-chidambaram-congress-resolution-palestine-cause-2448241-2023-10-13%5C%22%3Estand%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20was%20different%20from%20Modi%E2%80%99s.%20It%20did%20condemn%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20but%20immediately%20called%20for%20a%20ceasefire%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20CWC%20calls%20for%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20and%20for%20negotiations%20to%20begin%20on%20all%20outstanding%20issues%20including%20the%20imperative%20issues%20that%20have%20given%20rise%20to%20the%20present%20conflict.%E2%80%9D%20It%20did%20not%20take%20time%20to%20ask%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20Palestinians%20to%20be%20respected%20and%20spoke%20for%20their%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAssam%20chief%20minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20compared%20the%20stand%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20with%20that%20of%20Pakistan.%20He%20taunted%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20who%20had%20talked%20about%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20Palestinians%20over%20their%20land%20and%20resources%20and%20said%20that%20all%20Indian%20prime%20ministers%20had%20stood%20firmly%20with%20Palestine%2C%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsharad-pawar-india-position-israel-palestine-conflict-himanta-sarma-says-think-ncp-chief-will-send-supriya-sule-to-gaza-to-fight-for-hamas-4494154%23%3A~%3Atext%3Dfight%2520for%2520Hamas.-%2C%2522I%2520think%2520Sharad%2520Pawar%2520will%2520send%2520Supriya%2520(Sule)%2520to%2Con%2520the%2520Israel%252DPalestine%2520issue.%5C%22%3Easking%3C%2Fa%3E%20Pawar%20to%20send%20his%20daughter%20Supriya%20Sule%20to%20fight%20for%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20BJP%20leader%2C%20Piyush%20Goyal%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CPawar%20ji%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20same%20government%20that%20shed%20tears%20on%20the%20Batla%20House%20encounter%20and%20slept%20while%20there%20were%20terror%20attacks%20on%20Indian%20soil%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIt%20is%20very%20disturbing%20when%20a%20senior%20leader%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPawarSpeaks%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40PawarSpeaks%3C%2Fa%3E%20ji%20makes%20preposterous%20statements%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20stand%20on%20a%20terror%20attack%20in%20Israel.%20The%20menace%20of%20terrorism%20has%20to%20be%20condemned%20in%20all%20forms%2C%20in%20any%20part%20of%20the%20world.%20It%20is%20a%20pity%20that%20a%20person%20who%20has%20been%20India%E2%80%99s%20Defence%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Piyush%20Goyal%20(%40PiyushGoyal)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPiyushGoyal%2Fstatus%2F1714613554110754820%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2018%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESupport%20for%20Palestine%20is%20being%20treated%20as%20support%20for%20terrorism.%20You%20can%20be%20booked%20or%20jailed%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F10%2F25%2Fpro-israel-rallies-allowed-in-india-but-palestine-solidarity-sees-crackdown%5C%22%3Esupporting%20Palestine%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India.%20Protests%20are%20not%20allowed%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20increasing%20support%20for%20Israel%20in%20India%20is%20in%20consonance%20with%20the%20rise%20of%20anti-Muslim%2C%20anti-minority%20politics%20represented%20by%20the%20BJP.%20The%20idea%20of%20Israel%20as%20a%20country%20in%20which%20Jews%20are%20first-class%20citizens%20and%20others%20second%20is%20attractive%20to%20the%20BJP%20supporters%2C%20who%20want%20Hindus%20to%20be%20treated%20similarly%20in%20India.%20They%20want%20India%20to%20become%20a%20majoritarian%20democracy%20like%20Israel.%20They%20also%20share%20the%20sentiments%20of%20Israeli%20Jews%20who%20consider%20Palestinians%20as%20lesser%20humans%20who%20are%20unlike%20them%20in%20all%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOutsiders%20are%20puzzled%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthediplomat.com%2F2022%2F12%2Findias-hindutva-proponents-and-zionist-israel-strange-bedfellows%2F%5C%22%3Esupport%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20or%20its%20parent%20body%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%2C%20for%20Israel.%20Did%20it%20not%20endorse%20the%20notion%20of%20the%20Nazi%20%E2%80%98Final%20Solution%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20Jewish%20question%3F%20How%20can%20it%20now%20justify%20its%20support%20for%20Jews%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20paradox%20can%20be%20explained%20by%20the%20RSS%20and%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20belief%20in%20the%20idea%20of%20dominance.%20They%20admire%20those%20who%20dominate%20and%20use%20violence%20to%20maintain%20their%20dominance%20over%20others.%20A%20hundred%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20Nazis%20were%20the%20dominant%20power.%20Now%20it%20is%20Israel.%20The%20RSS%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fhistory%2Frss-golwalkar-links-nazism%5C%22%3Eworshipped%20Hitler%3C%2Fa%3E%20then%2C%20now%20it%20is%20a%20disciple%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fthe-israel-palestine-war-is-a-stain-on-every-one-of-us%5C%22%3EThe%20Israel-Palestine%20War%20Is%20a%20Stain%20on%20Every%20One%20of%20Us%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMy%20journalist%20friend%20was%20also%20perturbed%20by%20the%20silence%20on%20campuses.%20Why%20is%20our%20youth%20not%20speaking%20out%3F%20There%20are%20many%20reasons.%20But%20one%20reason%20is%20that%20they%20are%20not%20adequately%20informed.%20They%20depend%20on%20TV%20Big%20Media%20and%20WhatsApp%20for%20inforamation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20even%20the%20nearly%20six-month-long%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20stir%20the%20imagination%20of%20the%20rest%20of%20India.%20There%20are%20hardly%20any%20public%20protests%20demanding%20peace%20there.%20It%20is%20impossible%20for%20them%20to%20think%20about%20Palestine.%20For%20them%2C%20there%20is%20an%20entity%20called%20Israel%20which%20is%20being%20threatened%20by%20terrorists%20led%20by%20Hamas.%20Palestine%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20exist%20in%20their%20imagination.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20people%20who%20invoke%20Gandhi%20and%20Nehru%20to%20speak%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20Palestinians.%20But%20a%20significant%20section%20of%20Hindus%20now%20believe%20that%20India%20has%20to%20correct%20the%20%E2%80%9Cwrongs%E2%80%9D%20committed%20by%20those%20great%20leaders.%20Israel%20is%20cited%20as%20an%20ideal%20in%20these%20circles.%20Its%20violent%20methods%20to%20control%20people%20perhaps%20appeal%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20there%20is%20no%20parallel%20education%20about%20liberation%20struggles%20in%20India.%20Given%20the%20shift%20in%20demographics%2C%20with%20NFHS-5%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fhalf-indias-population-under-age-30-nfhs-explained-7910458%2F%5C%22%3Erevealing%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2052%25%20of%20Indians%20are%20under%20the%20age%20of%2030%2C%20present-day%20Indians%20do%20not%20have%20a%20memory%20of%20apartheid%20South%20Africa%20and%20know%20little%20of%20the%20stellar%20role%20India%E2%80%99s%20political%20leadership%20took%20in%20mobilising%20international%20opinion%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20that%2C%20one%20needs%20to%20accept%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20Indians%20are%20not%20averse%20to%20some%20kind%20of%20apartheid%20as%20they%20themselves%20believe%20in%20a%20caste-segregated%20society%2C%20with%20entrenched%20notions%20of%20hierarchy%20and%20dominance.%20Israel%20has%20achieved%20this.%20It%20may%2C%20therefore%2C%20be%20a%20reflex%20to%20admire%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698240954000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25174409%2Fimage-1432.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fisrael-palestine-conflict-india-forsakerole-voice-of-moderation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20increasing%20support%20for%20Israel%20in%20the%20country%20is%20in%20consonance%20with%20the%20rise%20of%20anti-Muslim%2C%20anti-minority%20politics%20represented%20by%20the%20BJP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl