n%20November%207%20and%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3EBaij%2C%20the%20sitting%20MP%20from%20Bastar%20who%20is%20contesting%20the%20state%20elections%20from%20Chitrakoot%20constituency%20this%20time%2C%20said%20that%20the%20party%20had%20decided%20to%20focus%20on%20%E2%80%9Cwinning%20candidates%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20decision.%20We%20have%20said%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%20that%20since%20a%20government%20has%20to%20be%20formed%20again%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20we%20will%20only%20give%20tickets%20to%20winning%20candidates.%20The%20high%20command%20and%20the%20party%20have%20taken%20this%20historic%20decision.%20We%20are%20all%20fighting%20together%20and%20we%20will%20form%20the%20government%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20differences%20within%20the%20party%20on%20account%20of%20the%20sitting%20MLAs%20being%20denied%20tickets%2C%20Baij%20said%20that%20discussions%20were%20held%20with%20those%20who%20were%20upset.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20some%20resentment%20%5Bamong%20the%20members%5D%20and%20that%20is%20natural.%20If%20someone%E2%80%99s%20ticket%20is%20cut%2C%20then%20they%20will%20feel%20upset%20and%20some%20resentment.%20But%20we%20have%20had%20discussions%20with%20everyone%20and%20spoken%20with%20them%20and%20no%20one%20will%20leave%20the%20party%20and%20everyone%20will%20help%20the%20party%20win%20the%20election%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20looking%20to%20retain%20power%20in%20the%20state%20after%20it%20trounced%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20the%202018%20elections.%20The%20saffron%20party%20had%20been%20in%20power%20in%20the%20state%20since%202003.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20won%2068%20of%20the%2090%20seats%20in%20the%202018%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBaij%20said%20that%20the%20party%20is%20looking%20to%20repeat%20such%20a%2