%3E%20%3Cp%3EBaij%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20raising%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdefame%E2%80%9D%20the%20Congress%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20has%20no%20issues%20to%20talk%20about.%20Through%20the%20ED%20and%20IT%2C%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20defame%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20government.%20Secondly%2C%20did%20scams%20not%20take%20place%20during%20the%2015%20years%20of%20BJP%20rule%3F%20Did%20the%20Rs%2036%2C000-crore%20PDS%20scam%20not%20take%20place%3F%20There%20were%20over%2050%20scams%20%E2%80%93%20small%20and%20big%20%E2%80%93%20under%20the%20BJP.%20The%20Union%20government%20should%20probe%20those%2C%20but%20they%20are%20not%20doing%20so.%20These%20allegations%20%5Bagainst%20the%20Congress%20government%5D%20do%20not%20have%20a%20grain%20of%20truth.%20Our%20government%20has%20done%20good%20work%20for%20the%20people%20and%20we%20will%20go%20to%20the%20people%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20this%20work%20and%20form%20the%20government%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20has%20not%20announced%20its%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%20in%20the%20state%2C%20raising%20questions%20about%20a%20leadership%20vacuum%20in%20the%20state%2C%20sitting%20Durg%20MP%20Vijay%20Baghel%20has%20been%20fielded%20to%20take%20on%20his%20uncle%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%2C%20in%20the%20Patan%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBhupesh%20Baghel%20is%20a%20five-time%20MLA%20from%20the%20area.%20His%20candidature%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20bid%20to%20woo%20voters%20from%20OBC%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBaij%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CBJP%20is%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20give%20us%20a%20direct%20fight%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20conduct%20a%20caste%20survey%20after%20coming%20to%20power%20and%20this%20will%20benefit%20those%20whose%20numbers%20are%20more%20but%20are%20not%20able%20to%20access%20the%20fruits%20of%20development.%20The%20chief%20minister%20is%20fighting%20from%20Patan%20and%20he%20will%20win%20with%20a%20record%20number%20of%20votes.%20There%20is%20no%20challenge%20and%20Vijay%20Baghel%E2%80%99s%20candidature%20will%20not%20make%20any%20difference%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Union%20government%20taking%20credit%20for%20our%20good%20work%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBaij%2C%20the%20Bastar%20MP%2C%20claimed%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20take%20credit%20for%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20government%E2%80%99s%20achievements%20in%20reducing%20Maoist%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnion%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20claim%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchhattisgarh-will-be-free-of-naxalism-if-bjp-comes-to-power-amit-shah-4496186%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Bastar%E2%80%99s%20Jagdalpur%20last%20week%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CIn%20nine%20years%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20incidents%20of%20(Naxal)%20violence%20declined%20by%2052%25%2C%20deaths%20(in%20Maoist%20violence)%20came%20down%20by%2070%25%2C%20civilian%20deaths%20decreased%20by%2068%25%2C%20while%20the%20(number%20of)%20Naxal-affected%20districts%20declined%20by%2062%25.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBaij%20said%20that%20peace%20in%20the%20Maoist-affected%20regions%20is%20due%20to%20the%20work%20done%20by%20the%20Congress%20government%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Union%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20take%20credit%20for%20the%20good%20work%20done%20by%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20government.%20These%20are%20double%20standards%20in%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20policies%20and%20this%20won%E2%80%99t%20work.%20Amit%20Shah%20says%20something%2C%20%5BBJP%20president%20J.P.%5D%20Nadda%20says%20something%20else.%20Different%20leaders%20are%20saying%20different%20things%20and%20they%20are%20not%20on%20the%20same%20page%20on%20this%20%5Bmatter%5D%20either.%20But%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20government%20has%20done%20good%20work%20and%20there%20is%20peace%20in%20Bastar%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Nadda%20had%20said%20that%20Naxal%20activities%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.economictimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fnaxal-incidents-have-increased-in-chhattisgarh-under-congress-rule-says-bjp-president-j-p-nadda%2Famp_articleshow%2F97826342.cms%5C%22%3Eincreased%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20under%20the%20Congress%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20independent%20India%2C%20residents%20of%20more%20than%20120%20villages%20in%20Bastar%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Felections%2Fchhattisgarh%2Fchhattisgarh-polls-residents-of-over-120-villages-in-maoist-hit-bastar-to-vote-in-their-own-villages-for-first-time-since-independence-2725287%5C%22%3Evote%20in%20their%20own%20settlements%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls.%20Polling%20stations%20will%20be%20set%20up%20in%20these%20places%2C%20which%20were%20earlier%20Maoist%20strongholds%2C%20and%20voters%20had%20to%20earlier%20trek%208-10%20kilometres%20to%20cast%20their%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBaij%20said%20that%20this%20development%20was%20made%20possible%20due%20to%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20Congress%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20government%20has%20worked%20to%20develop%20those%20interior%20villages%20where%20rations%20would%20not%20reach%2C%20where%20there%20was%20no%20electricity%2C%20water%2C%20roads%2C%20hospitals%2C%20and%20schools.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20there%20is%20peace%20in%20these%20areas%20now.%20They%20will%20vote%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20Adivasis%2C%20our%20government%20has%20worked%20very%20well%20and%20we%20will%20plan%20better%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years.%20In%20these%20interior%20villages%2C%20the%20BJP%20did%20not%20open%20ration%20shops%2C%20did%20not%20help%20people%20with%20receiving%20their%20Aadhaar%20cards%2C%20and%20did%20not%20provide%20electricity%2C%20health%2C%20and%20education.%20Our%20government%20has%20delivered%20%3Cem%3Evikas%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5Bprogress%5D.%20We%20have%20opened%20ration%20shops.%20There%20were%20none.%20We%20have%20made%20Aadhaar%20cards%20for%20people.%20We%20have%20built%20schools%20and%20hospitals.%20If%20the%20BJP%20thinks%20they%20have%20constructed%20a%20building%20on%20the%20roads%20initially%20built%20by%20us%20and%20calling%20it%20%3Cem%3Evikas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20then%20good%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20security%20situation%20in%20these%20villages%2C%20Baij%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Ctight%20security%E2%80%9D%20measures%20have%20been%20implemented%20and%20camps%20have%20been%20set%20up%20to%20ensure%20a%20peaceful%20polling%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698238855000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25182130%2FF8-AIk5bsAAg7Ie.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-chhattisgarh-party-chief-deepak-baij-interview-elections%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Deepak%20Baij%20has%20defended%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20not%20give%20tickets%20to%2022%20sitting%20MLAs%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20elections%20scheduled%20for%20next%20month.%20He%20was%20confident%20that%20the%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20government%20would%20retain%20power.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-chhattisgarh-party-chief-deepak-baij-interview-elections%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Did%20A%20Prominent%20Demographer%2C%20Responsible%20for%20NFHS%2C%20Get%20Victimised%20Due%20to%20'Inconvenient%20Data'%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25180502%2Fimage_6487327.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20country%20as%20big%20as%20India%2C%20data%20on%20utilisation%20of%20various%20schemes%20is%20very%20important.%20Governments%20%E2%80%93%20both%20central%20and%20state%20%E2%80%93%20make%20a%20number%20of%20schemes%20targeting%20specific%20populations%2C%20and%20then%20make%20various%20claims%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20success%20of%20these%20schemes.%20And%2C%20that%20is%20where%20the%20data%20assumes%20a%20lot%20of%20importance%2C%20as%20it%20is%20data%20only%20which%20helps%20understand%20the%20%E2%80%98success%E2%80%99%20of%20these%20interventions%20worth%20crores%20of%20taxpayer%E2%80%99s%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHowever%20data%20in%20India%20is%20facing%20assaults%20of%20various%20kinds%20%E2%80%93%20be%20it%20the%20one%20emanating%20from%20international%20agencies%20or%20the%20ones%20made%20by%20Indian%20ones.%20One%20such%20recent%20example%20was%20the%20institute%20%E2%80%93%20International%20Institute%20of%20Population%20Sciences%20%E2%80%94%20which%20prepares%20the%20Nation%20Family%20Health%20Surveys%20(NFHSs).%20In%20July%20this%20year%2C%20Union%20health%20ministry%20suspended%20the%20head%20of%20IIPS%2C%20K%20S%20James%2C%20as%20it%20found%20certain%20%E2%80%98complaints%E2%80%99%20against%20him%2C%20%E2%80%98prima%20facie%E2%80%99%2C%20true.%20The%20government%20said%20it%20wanted%20to%20investigate%20those%20charges%20and%20hence%20his%20suspension%20pending%20inquiry%20was%20necessary.%20On%20October%2011%2C%20his%20suspension%20was%20revoked.%20He%20was%20reinstated%20as%20IIPS%20director%2C%20and%20then%20his%20resignation%2C%20that%20he%20had%20tendered%20on%20August%208%2C%20was%20accepted.%20And%20all%20of%20this%20happened%20in%20a%20span%20of%20one%20hour%20on%20the%20same%20day.%20What%20happened%20between%20July%20and%20October%2C%20and%20did%20anything%20come%20out%20in%20the%20inquiry%3F%20To%20know%20this%2C%20and%20more%2C%20watch%20this%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20NFHS-5%20had%20showed%20that%20the%20prevalence%20of%20anaemia%20had%20gone%20up%20despite%20several%20schemes%2C%20that%20India%20was%20nowhere%20close%20to%20being%20open%20defecation%20free%20and%20that%20more%20than%20half%20the%20rural%20women%20did%20not%20have%20access%20to%20a%20cylinder%20despite%20a%20scheme%20dedicated%20for%20this%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FJHxXCEIKBMA%3Fsi%3Dq11rBUMxbaA3r8pD%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698238836000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25180502%2Fimage_6487327.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fdid-a-prominent-demographer-responsible-for-nfhs-get-victimised-due-to-inconvenient-data%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20NFHS-5%20had%20showed%20that%20the%20prevalence%20of%20anaemia%20had%20gone%20up%20despite%20several%20schemes%20among%20other%20unsatisfactory%20outcomes%20for%20the%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fdid-a-prominent-demographer-responsible-for-nfhs-get-victimised-due-to-inconvenient-data%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Did%20A%20Prominent%20Demographer%2C%20Responsible%20for%20NFHS%2C%20Get%20Victimised%20Due%20to%20'Inconvenient%20Data'%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25180502%2Fimage_6487327.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20country%20as%20big%20as%20India%2C%20data%20on%20utilisatio