nsions%20escalated%20further%20on%20October%2019%2C%20after%20Canada%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-calls-canadas-consulate-move-unilateral-clarifies-parity-only-for-diplomats-in-capitals%5C%22%3Ecomplied%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20demand%20to%20withdraw%3C%2Fa%3E%2041%20diplomats%20posted%20in%20India%2C%20suspending%20consular%20services%20in%20Chandigarh%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Bengaluru.%20This%20is%20likely%20to%20cause%20delays%20in%20visa%20services%20and%20longer%20waits%20at%20the%20Canadian%20Embassy%20in%20New%20Delhi%20for%20in-person%20submissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESimran%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20of%20now%2C%20my%20parents%20have%20asked%20me%20to%20first%20complete%20my%20IELTS%20coaching%20and%20get%20a%20good%20score.%20We%20will%20plan%20the%20study%20visa%20later.%20If%20the%20situation%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20does%20not%20improve%20by%20then%2C%20I%20will%20have%20to%20pursue%20graduation%20in%20Jalandhar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20IELTS%20test%20scores%20are%20valid%20for%20two%20years%2C%20Simran%20said%20many%20of%20her%20friends%20are%20also%20planning%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccomplete%20the%20exam%20first%20and%20then%20wait%20for%20the%20right%20time%20to%20apply%20for%20a%20study%20visa%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fpunjab-india-canada-standoff-sparks-visa-fears-among-students-overseas-consultants%5C%22%3EPunjab%3A%20India-Canada%20Standoff%20Sparks%20Visa%20Fears%20Among%20Students%2C%20Overseas%20Consultants%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20those%20who%20visited%20the%20Canadian%20consulate%20in%20Chandigarh%20on%20October%2019%20to%20avail%20of%20services%20were%20turned%20back.%20Applicants%20also%20say%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findia-canada-fake-news-punjabis-visa%5C%22%3Efake%20news%20about%20the%20issue%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20worsening%20the%20confusion%20and%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20student%20Sunaina%2C%20who%20was%20taking%20IELTS%20coaching%20from%20an%20institute%20in%20Phagwara%20in%20the%20Kapurthala%20district%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CStudy%20visas%20are%20time-bound%2C%20as%20the%20students%20get%20admission%20according%20to%20the%20seat%20availability%20in%20the%20next%20semester%20and%20pay%20a%20hefty%20fee%20in%20dollars.%20We%20are%20deeply%20concerned.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESunaina%E2%80%99s%20village%20in%20Jalandhar%2C%20Ganna%2C%20has%20high%20levels%20of%20drug%20abuse%2C%20petty%20crime%2C%20and%20violence.%20Parents%20prefer%20to%20send%20their%20children%20abroad%20for%20education%20so%20that%20they%20can%20escape%20these%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20village%20is%20infamous%20as%20a%20haven%20for%20drug%20peddlers.%20Hardly%20a%20day%20passes%20when%20we%20do%20not%20witness%20petty%20crime%2C%20police%20raids%2C%20and%20arrests%20of%20drug%20peddlers%20or%20fights%20in%20the%20streets.%20People%20in%20our%20village%20have%20either%20moved%20to%20the%20cities%20or%20emigrated.%20The%20lack%20of%20quality%20jobs%20and%20wages%20is%20a%20huge%20concern%20too.%20Youth%20today%20want%20value%20for%20the%20money%20invested%20in%20education%2C%20which%20is%20assured%20if%20you%20move%20abroad%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEducation%20consultants%20worried%20over%20visa%20delays%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20withdrawing%2041%20diplomats%20from%20India%2C%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20immigration%20minister%20Marc%20Miller%20said%20that%20Canada%20would%20continue%20to%20accept%20and%20process%20all%20temporary%20and%20permanent%20resident%20applications%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20also%20informed%20that%20the%20remaining%20staff%20will%20continue%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20work%20that%20cannot%20be%20moved%20out%20of%20the%20country%2C%20such%20as%20urgent%20cases%2C%20visa%20printing%2C%20and%20working%20with%20visa%20application%20centres%20and%20the%20panel%20physicians%20who%20conduct%20the%20important%20immigration%20medical%20examination%20for%20the%20applicants.%20%E2%80%9CVisa%20application%20centres%20are%20run%20by%20third-party%20contractors%20(VFS%20Global)%20and%20would%20not%20be%20affected%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F21173817%2F1024px-The_Prime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_with_the_Prime_Minister_of_Canada_Mr._Justin_Trudeau_at_Hyderabad_House_in_New_Delhi_on_February_23_2018_1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F21173817%2F1024px-The_Prime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_with_the_Prime_Minister_of_Canada_Mr._Justin_Trudeau_at_Hyderabad_House_in_New_Delhi_on_February_23_2018_1.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F21173817%2F1024px-The_Prime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_with_the_Prime_Minister_of_Canada_Mr._Justin_Trudeau_at_Hyderabad_House_in_New_Delhi_on_February_23_2018_1-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F21173817%2F1024px-The_Prime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_with_the_Prime_Minister_of_Canada_Mr._Justin_Trudeau_at_Hyderabad_House_in_New_Delhi_on_February_23_2018_1-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-674144%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJustin%20Trudeau%20and%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Photo%3A%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20GODL-India%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20education%20consultants%20say%20fewer%20diplomatic%20staff%20in%20India%20and%20the%20suspension%20of%20consular%20services%20in%20three%20major%20cities%20will%20inevitably%20mean%20an%20increase%20in%20visa%20processing%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKuljit%20Hayer%2C%20who%20owns%20Jalandhar-based%20Universal%20Travels%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20diplomatic%20staff%20reduced%20to%20just%20one-third%2C%20the%20processing%20time%20of%20applications%20will%20be%20longer.%20The%20impact%20would%20not%20be%20limited%20to%20student%20visa%20cases%20but%20to%20visitor%20visa%20and%20Permanent%20Residency%20(PR)%20applications%20too.%20Basically%2C%20Punjabis%20will%20suffer%20in%20both%20cases%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20it%20is%20because%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20suspension%20of%20visa%20services%20to%20Canadian%20citizens%20or%20those%20applying%20for%20visas%20from%20India.%20However%2C%20given%20the%20current%20scenario%2C%20the%20Canadian%20government%20may%20focus%20more%20on%20study%20visas%2C%20as%20they%20are%20time-bound%20and%20subject%20to%20a%20student%E2%80%99s%20admission%20in%20a%20college%20or%20university.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHayer%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20downturn%20in%20diplomatic%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20have%20resulted%20in%20a%20loss%20of%20business%20to%20travel%20agents.%20%E2%80%9COvernight%20250%20to%20300%20air%20tickets%20were%20cancelled%20in%20the%20past%20few%20days.%20Many%20families%20had%20to%20postpone%20weddings%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20completely%20suspended%20visas%20for%20Canadian%20citizens%2C%20the%20Canadian%20government%E2%80%99s%20work%20will%20be%20slower%20now.%20We%20can%20just%20hope%20that%20this%20situation%20improves%20gradually.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Mass%20rejections%20unlikely%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Pamsy%20Singh%20Sehmbey%2C%20a%20consultant%20based%20in%20Toronto%2C%20said%20that%20despite%20the%20recent%20escalation%2C%20the%20Canadian%20authorities%20were%20in%20no%20mood%20to%20ruin%20their%20relations%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCanadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Trudeau%20has%20made%20this%20clear.%20There%20might%20be%20some%20delay%20in%20the%20processing%20time%20of%20applications%2C%20but%20I%20am%20sure%20it%20will%20not%20lead%20to%20mass%20rejection%20of%20visas.%20Even%20now%2C%20the%20processing%20time%20for%20study%20visas%20is%20around%2022%20days%2C%20and%2031%20days%20for%20visitor%20visas.%20The%20dates%20for%20biometric%20services%2C%20which%20are%20mandatory%20for%20Canadian%20visas%2C%20are%20easily%20available%20at%20VFS%20Global%2C%20a%20third-party%20service.%20Similarly%2C%20dates%20for%20medical%20tests%20for%20visas%20are%20also%20available%20as%20per%20schedule.%20I%20think%20people%20should%20keep%20applying%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EContrary%20to%20this%2C%20Kanwaljit%20Kaur%2C%20branch%20manager%20of%20Golden%20Pillars%20Immigration%20in%20Jalandhar%2C%20said%20that%20ever%20since%20Canada%20was%20asked%20to%20withdraw%2041%20diplomats%2C%20prospective%20applicants%20are%20thinking%20twice%20because%20they%20fear%20an%20unexplained%20rejection.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSee%2C%20nobody%20wants%20their%20visa%20application%20rejected.%20As%20of%20now%2C%20people%20have%20stopped%20applying%20for%20Canadian%20visas.%20Since%20the%20Canadian%20authorities%20have%20said%20there%20might%20be%20an%20increase%20in%20processing%20time%2C%20people%20are%20concerned.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20processing%20time%20for%20study%20visas%20was%20around%2015%20to%2030%20days.%20However%2C%20it%20might%20go%20up%20to%20two%20months.%20We%20are%20suggesting%20clients%20wait%20for%20now%2C%20as%20Canada%20did%20not%20stop%20issuing%20visas%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20We%20would%20request%20people%20to%20remain%20aware%20of%20the%20latest%20updates%20and%20beware%20of%20fake%20news%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeddings%20cancelled%20and%20businesses%20affected%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20Jalandhar-based%20couple%2C%20Sandeep%20Singh%20and%20Sandeep%20Kaur%2C%20said%20their%20Canadian%20cousin%20was%20supposed%20to%20get%20married%20on%20October%2021.%20The%20groom%20failed%20to%20get%20a%20visa%20following%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20suspension%20of%20visa%20services%20to%20Canadian%20citizens%20and%20the%20ceremony%20had%20to%20be%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNearly%20half%20of%20the%20groom%E2%80%99s%20relatives%20are%20based%20in%20the%20US%20and%20others%20are%20in%20the%20UK.%20Almost%20all%20of%20them%20had%20booked%20air%20tickets%20for%20the%20wedding%20in%20Hoshiarpur%20district.%20They%20had%20to%20postpone%20the%20wedding.%20The%20groom%E2%80%99s%20family%20had%20printed%20the%20wedding%20cards%20while%20the%20bride%E2%80%99s%20family%20had%20booked%20the%20marriage%20palace.%20It%20led%20to%20a%20big%20financial%20loss%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sandeep%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESingh%20said%20that%20the%20bride%20and%20the%20groom%E2%80%99s%20families%20were%20eagerly%20waiting%20for%20India-Canada%20relations%20to%20normalise.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20hope%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20reconsiders%20its%20decision%20and%20allows%20People%20of%20Indian%20Origin%20(PIOs)%20to%20visit%20their%20homeland%20for%20reunions%2C%20weddings%2C%20and%20functions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20regions%20of%20Jalandhar%2C%20Kapurthala%2C%20Hoshiarpur%2C%20and%20Nawanshahr%20%E2%80%93%20which%20have%20a%20sizeable%20number%20of%20Punjabis%20settled%20in%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20Canada%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20Europe%20%E2%80%93%20are%20famous%20for%20hiring%20private%20jets%2C%20luxury%20wedding%20cars%2C%20Punjabi%20singers%2C%20bhangra%20groups%20and%20hotels%20for%20weddings%20and%20other%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20usually%20busy%20NRI%20markets%20of%20Jalandhar%2C%20Phagwara%2C%20and%20Ludhiana%20have%20been%20bearing%20the%20brunt%20of%20fewer%20visitors.%20%E2%80%9COur%20business%20has%20been%20badly%20affected.%20The%20onset%20of%20winter%20in%20Punjab%20means%20NRI%20and%20PIO%20season%20for%20us.%20We%20look%20forward%20to%20a%20big%20boost%20in%20revenue%2C%20as%20weddings%2C%20functions%2C%20and%20family%20visits%20take%20place%20from%20October%20to%20April.%20However%2C%20this%20year%2C%20the%20market%20is%20slow%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Vidya%20Sagar%20from%20Madaan%20Cloth%20House%2C%20Phagwara.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20showroom%20owner%2C%20also%20from%20Phagwara%2C%20said%20that%20an%20NRI%20wedding%20means%20flourishing%20business%20for%20every%20sector.%20The%20owner%20cited%20the%20example%20of%20a%20UK-based%20that%20landed%20in%20Jalandhar%20for%20a%20wedding%20last%20year.%20%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20did%20they%20buy%20traditional%20dresses%20and%20jewellery%20worth%20several%20lakhs%2C%20but%20they%20stayed%20in%20three%20of%20the%20top%20hotels%20of%20Jalandhar%2C%20spending%20a%20whopping%20amount.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698233106000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F14133234%2F40.-Travel-agencies_-India.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fpunjab-india-canada-row-visa-delays-students-business-losses%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Canada%20suspended%20consular%20services%20in%20Chandigarh%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Bengaluru%20after%2041%20of%20its%20diplomats%20were%20asked%20to%20leave%20by%20India.%20This%20has%20only%20further%20worsened%20the%20fears%20of%20students%20as%20well%20as%20businesses%20looking%20forward%20to%20'NRI%20season'%20in%20Punjab.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fpunjab-india-canada-row-visa-delays-students-business-losses%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hospitals%20in%20Gaza%20forced%20to%20shut%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20fuel%20as%20