20concerning%20propaganda%20in%20Indian%20right-wing%20spaces.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20been%20a%20definite%20tendency%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%20in%20India%20to%20try%20to%20incorporate%20global%20events%20into%20the%20constant%20narrative%20that%20paints%20mostly%20Muslims%20but%20sometimes%20even%20moderate%20Hindus%20as%20an%20enemy%20or%20a%20threat%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Waghre.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20this%2C%20Waghre%20said%2C%20was%20owing%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Creligious%20angle%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20conflict%20between%20the%20Jewish%20state%20of%20Israel%20and%20the%20Muslim-dominated%20Palestine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20author%20accessed%2013%20WhatsApp%20groups%2C%20all%20of%20them%20expressing%20clear%20support%20for%20the%20Hindutva%20ideology%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20RSS%20through%20the%20names%20of%20the%20groups%20as%20well%20as%20the%20display%20photos%2C%20generally%20featuring%20images%20of%20Modi%20and%20Adityanath.%20The%20groups%20are%20not%20being%20named%20to%20protect%20the%20author%E2%80%99s%20access.%20The%20number%20of%20members%20in%20these%20groups%20range%20from%20anywhere%20around%2050%20to%20nearly%20400.%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20author%20accessed%20multiple%20Facebook%20groups%20and%20pages%2C%20which%20displayed%20open%20affiliations%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBroadly%2C%20much%20of%20the%20propaganda%20in%20these%20groups%20falls%20under%20four%20different%20themes%20%E2%80%93%20from%20dehumanising%20Palestinian%20suffering%20and%20delegitimising%20support%20for%20them%2C%20to%20making%20the%20Israel-Gaza%20war%20relatable%20by%20drawing%20historical%20Indian%20comparisons%20to%20it%2C%20to%20warning%20Hindus%20about%20an%20Islamist%20attack%20and%20pitching%20the%20BJP%20and%20Modi%20as%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20only%20hope%20to%20fight%20this.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Just%20like%20Kashmiri%20Hindus%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20significant%20proportion%20of%20messages%20on%20these%20groups%20attempts%20to%20try%20and%20make%20the%20war%20more%20relevant%20to%20an%20Indian%20audience.%20It%20does%20this%20by%20drawing%20parallels%20to%20the%20situation%2C%20but%20selectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20plight%20of%20Israelis%2C%20these%20messages%20insist%2C%20is%20like%20Kashmiri%20Hindus.%20Circulating%20a%20video%2C%20ostensibly%20of%20an%20Israeli%20family%20held%20hostage%20by%20Hamas%20terrorists%2C%20the%20message%20asks%20readers%20to%20%E2%80%9Clook%20at%20the%20fear%E2%80%9D%20on%20their%20faces.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20same%20what%20Kashmiri%20Hindus%20faced%20in%201990%20(sic)%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20message%20says.%20The%20purpose%20behind%20the%20comparison%20becomes%20clear%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20message%3A%20%E2%80%9CIndian%20wokes%20will%20call%20it%20RSS%20propoganda%2C%20in%20reality%20ISLAM%20IS%20PEACE%20LOVING%20RELIGION%20(sic)%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20says%2C%20sarcastically.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20467px)%2085vw%2C%20467px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25160607%2FKashmiri-Hindus.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22467%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25160607%2FKashmiri-Hindus.png%20467w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25160607%2FKashmiri-Hindus-170x300.png%20170w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681666%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22824%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Hamas%20is%20equated%20to%20%E2%80%9CIslamic%20invaders%E2%80%9D%20like%20Humayun%20and%20Babur%2C%20both%20of%20them%20ostensibly%20attacking%20non-Muslims%20with%20similar%20brutality.%20The%20corollary%20of%20these%20comparisons%20comes%20in%20a%20later%20bunch%20of%20messaging%3A%20referring%20to%20the%20violence%20by%20Hamas%2C%20the%20messages%20would%20remind%