5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25154551%2FScreenshot-2023-10-25-at-3.45.15-PM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25154551%2FScreenshot-2023-10-25-at-3.45.15-PM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25154551%2FScreenshot-2023-10-25-at-3.45.15-PM-300x188.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25154551%2FScreenshot-2023-10-25-at-3.45.15-PM-1024x642.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681656%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22752%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20selfie%20point%20at%20Rajghat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20joint%20venture%20between%20the%20IA%20and%20the%20United%20Services%20Institution%20(USI)%20think%20tank%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Udbhav%20aims%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleseDetailm.aspx%3FPRID%3D1969684%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%20(PIB)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20exploit%20India%E2%80%99s%205%2C000-year%20old%20civilisational%20legacy%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccomprehend%20its%20enduring%20connect%2C%20relevance%20and%20applicability%20in%20the%20modern%20day%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20bequest%20includes%20studying%2C%20examining%20and%20analysing%20the%20writings%20of%20Chanakya%20(%3Cem%3EArthashastra%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20post-Mauryan%20Kamandaka%20(%3Cem%3ENitisara%3C%2Fem%3E)%20and%20those%20of%20the%20Tamil%20saint-poet%20Thiruvalluvar%20(%3Cem%3ETirukkural%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20all%20of%20which%20the%20PIB%20incredulously%20declared%20%E2%80%9C%5Balign%5D%20with%20modern%20military%20codes%20of%20ethics%20or%20just%20war%20and%20principles%20of%20the%20Geneva%20Convention%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20goes%20on%20to%20state%20that%20Udbhav%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvisionary%20initiative%20by%20the%20%5BIA%5D%E2%80%9D%20seeking%20to%20%E2%80%9Cintegrate%20age-old%20wisdom%20with%20contemporary%20military%20pedagogy%E2%80%9D%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20enhancing%20%E2%80%9Cstrategic%20thinking%2C%20statecraft%20and%20warfare%E2%80%9D.%20In%20short%2C%20Udbhav%2C%20according%20to%20the%20MoD%20and%20the%20government%2C%20is%20poised%20to%20%E2%80%9Cfoster%20deeper%20understanding%E2%80%9D%20of%20military%20matters%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccontribute%20to%20enriching%20military%20curricula%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Findian-army-operation-udbhav%5C%22%3EWhat%20India%E2%80%99s%20Military%20Is%20Taking%20From%20%E2%80%98Ancient%20Traditions%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20and%20What%20it%20Should%20Be%20Learning%20Instead%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20IA%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20General%20Manoj%20Pande%2C%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%20V.R.%20Chaudhuri%20and%20a%20host%20of%20three-star%20officers%20from%20all%20three%20services%20attended%20Udbhav%E2%80%99s%20launch%20at%20the%20Indian%20Military%20Heritage%20Festival%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20IA%20officers%2C%20like%20retired%20Major%20General%20B.S.%20Dhanoa%2C%20who%20is%20on%20the%20faculty%20of%20the%20Naval%20War%20College%20at%20Mandovi%20in%20Goa%2C%20strongly%20disagree.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAncient%20wisdom%20should%20not%20be%20sought%20to%20tackle%20modern-day%20contingencies%2C%20even%20if%20their%20study%20brings%20solace%20to%20the%20restlessness%20in%20our%20mind%20to%20try%20and%20decipher%20what%20our%20ancestors%20opted%20to%20do%20on%20the%20battlefield%20in%20a%20long%20gone%20epoch%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FF9F19rDXgAA7xv4%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20the%20former%20armoured%20corps%20officer%20in%20a%20recent%20op-ed%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20fascination%20with%20the%20study%20of%20ancient%20texts%20is%20at%20best%20an%20academic%20exercise%20in%20self-pride%2C%20he%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20the%20two-star%20officer%20chidingly%20added%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdulcet%20tones%20of%20ancient%20poetry%E2%80%9D%20should%20not%20%E2%80%9Cseduce%E2%80%9D%20people%20into%20believing%20that%20what%20had%20so%20far%20been%20practised%20in%20planning%20and%20executing%20Indian%20military%20strategy%20was%20%E2%80%9Csub-par%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cirrelevant%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Crelegated%20to%20a%20distant%20memory%20with%20rediscovered%20ancient%20wisdom%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNothing%E2%80%9D%2C%20said%20General%20Dhanoa%2C%20%E2%80%9Ccould%20be%20further%20from%20the%20truth%20in%20the%20framing%20of%20modern-day%20military%20strategy%20and%20the%20need%20to%20have%20a%20common%20doctrinal%20thread%20that%20binds%20the%20tactical%20to%20the%20strategic%20in%20our%20expected%20joint%20theatre%20commands%20of%20the%20future.%E2%80%9D%20Besides%2C%20there%20was%20a%20need%20to%20remain%20alive%20to%20the%20doctrinal%20precepts%20of%20modern-day%20conflict%20that%20required%20%E2%80%9Ckeen%20study%20of%20current%20military%20thought%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20categorically%20advised.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20earlier%2C%20the%20MoD%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdefence-ministry-selfie-points-narendra-modi%5C%22%3Edirected%20the%20establishment%20of%20geo-tagged%20selfie%20points%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20all%20its%20various%20departments%20and%20related%20organisations%20to%20%E2%80%98showcase%E2%80%99%20the%20achievements%20or%20good%20works%20executed%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20the%20military%20realm%20over%20the%20past%20nine%20years%20it%20had%20been%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20822%20such%20selfie%20points%2C%20that%20were%20likely%20to%20carry%20a%20photograph%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20much%20like%20the%20former%20COVID-19%20vaccine%20certificates%20and%20more%20recently%20like%20the%20G20%20posters%2C%20which%20also%20sported%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20lotus%20logo%2C%20would%20be%20focused%20on%20Defence%20Public%20Sector%20Undertakings%2C%20the%20Border%20Roads%20Organisation%2C%20the%20Indian%20Coast%20Guard%2C%20the%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%2C%20Sainik%20Schools%20and%20the%20National%20Cadet%20Corps%2C%20amongst%20other%20military%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FC_kL-3vCius%3Fsi%3Dm2-WbidFlOBU00tH%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20231013115245%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fcgda.nic.in%2Fadm%2Fcircular%2FAN-III-Selfie-101023.pdf%5C%22%3EIn%20its%20October%209%20directive%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20MoD%20had%20declared%20that%20these%20selfie%20points%20would%20be%20erected%20at%20%E2%80%9Cprominent%20locations%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmaximum%20footfall%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20potential%20of%20attracting%20public%20attention%2C%20like%20war%20memorials%2C%20rail%20and%20metro%20stations%2C%20bus%20terminals%2C%20airports%2C%20malls%2C%20schools%20and%20colleges%20and%20even%20festival%20gatherings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20MoD%20had%20also%20suggested%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfeedback%20mechanism%E2%80%9D%2C%20including%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdedicated%20app%E2%80%9D%20which%20would%20enable%20people%20to%20upload%20their%20selfies%20as%20well%20as%20posting%20them%20on%20exclusive%20handles%20on%20X%2C%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%20to%20further%20transmit%20and%20perpetuate%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20message%20in%20the%20election%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20May%2C%20IA%20Headquarters%20in%20Delhi%20had%20officially%20%E2%80%98recommended%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20a%20services%20euphemism%20for%20%E2%80%98ordered%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-encourages-soldiers-to-undertake-social-service-during-leave-contribute-to-nation-building-effort-101693765707394.html%5C%22%3Ethat%20all%20soldiers%20on%20home%20leave%20propagate%20%E2%80%9Cnation%20building%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20endeavours%20in%20their%20respective%20village%2C%20small%20town%20and%20city%20neighbourhood%20communities%20by%20publicising%20the%20merits%20of%20assorted%20government%20welfare%20schemes%20like%20the%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Abhiyan%20and%20Sarva%20Shiksha%20Abhiyan%20and%20many%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%20would%20be%20monitored%20by%20the%20soldiers%E2%80%99%20units%20through%20quarterly%20feedback%20supported%20by%20photographs%20and%20video%20clips.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20these%20%E2%80%98soldier%20ambassadors%E2%80%99%20have%20been%20asked%20by%20the%20IA%E2%80%99s%20Ceremonials%20and%20Welfare%20Directorate%20that%20functions%20under%20the%20adjutant%20general%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20responsible%20for%20the%20forces%E2%80%99%20overall%20administration%2C%20to%20instruct%20their%20respective%20societies%20in%20patriotism%20and%20nationalism%2C%20hygiene%2C%20cleanliness%2C%20the%20perils%20of%20drug%20abuse%2C%20road%20safety%2C%20to%20motivate%20and%20mentor%20their%20youth%20and%20to%20organise%20sports%20events%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESenior%20military%20officials%20said%20that%20the%20Army%20Training%20Command%20in%20Shimla%20had%20issued%20formal%20guidelines%20for%20these%20soldiers%20to%20follow%20with%20regard%20to%20vindicating%20these%20%E2%80%98educative%E2%80%99%20tasks%2C%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20%E2%80%98leveraging%E2%80%99%20their%20skills%20and%20innate%20discipline%20towards%20augmenting%20nation%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Panag%20estimates%20that%20at%20any%20given%20time%2C%20the%20armed%20forces%20will%20have%20some%20350%2C000%20%E2%80%9Csocial%20warriors%E2%80%9D%20engaged%20in%20various%20welfare%20activities%20at%20a%20time%2C%20in%20what%20he%20terms%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Farmy-cant-ask-soldiers-to-do-social-work-on-leave-its-beyond-the-call-of-duty%2F1750131%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cbiggest%20government-led%20social%20service%20drive%20ever%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20soldiers%20are%20entitled%20to%20two%20months%20leave%20annually%2C%20in%20addition%20to%2030%20days%20of%20casual%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fpoliticising-the-armed-forces-has-consequences%5C%22%3EPoliticising%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20Has%20Consequences%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20goes%20on%20to%20state%20that%20this%20scheme%20was%20being%20%E2%80%98forced%E2%80%99%20on%20soldiers%2C%20or%20an%20advisory%20would%20have%20sufficed%2C%20rather%20than%20structured%20directions%20to%20implement%20it.%20In%20military%20culture%2C%20the%20general%20says%2C%20recommendations%20of%20higher%20headquarters%20were%20tantamount%20to%20%E2%80%98orders%20to%20be%20obeyed%E2%80%99%20and%20argued%20that%20words%20had%20been%20cleverly%20juggled%20to%20make%20the%20scheme%20appear%20voluntary%20to%20ward%20off%20protests%20and%20court%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20adage%20that%20a%20soldier%20is%20never%20off%20duty%2C%20has%20been%20literally%20applied%E2%80%9D%2C%20General%20Panag%20said%20and%20dubbed%20the%20%E2%80%98social%20warrior%E2%80%99%20scheme%20as%20%E2%80%9Ccontroversial%20both%20in%20concept%20and%20execution%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20wider%20canvas%2C%20the%20Faustian%20bargain%20between%20the%20Indian%20soldier%20and%20politicians%20had%20intensified%20manifold%20in%20recent%20years.%20It%20is%20no%20secret%20that%20many%20senior%20service%20personnel%20are%20increasingly%20identifying%20themselves%20with%20the%20BJP-led%20administration%2C%20that%20in%20turn%2