%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20happening%20due%20to%20a%20number%20of%20factors%20including%20the%20rising%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20job%20losses%2C%20and%20the%20economic%20slowdown%2C%20the%20report%20added%2C%20citing%20an%20analyst.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20ICICI%20Bank%20and%20Bajaj%20Finance%20are%20closely%20monitoring%20this%20segment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20our%20portfolio%20is%20concerned%2C%20we%20have%20a%20very%20minimal%20presence%20in%20the%20smaller%20ticket%20size%20segment.%20But%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20monitor%20this%20as%20we%20go%20along%2C%E2%80%9D%20Anindya%20Banerjee%2C%20chief%20financial%20officer%20at%20ICICI%20Bank%2C%20told%20analysts%20on%2021%20October%2C%20per%3Cem%3E%20Mint%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20consumption%20might%20be%20impacted%20if%20people%20stopped%20getting%20these%20loans%2C%20Madan%20Sabnavis%2C%20chief%20economist%20of%20Bank%20of%20Baroda%2C%20told%20the%20newspaper.%20In%20such%20a%20case%2C%20%E2%80%9Cpeople%20will%20look%20for%20other%20avenues%2C%20some%20much%20costlier%20than%20bank%20credit%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20August%2C%20total%20personal%20loans%20or%20%E2%80%9Cother%20personal%20loans%E2%80%9D%20as%20classified%20by%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20stood%20at%20%3Cspan%3ERs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E12.2%20trillion%2C%20up%2026%25%20from%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20the%20business%20daily%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698219035000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F20192652%2Findia-g7d34db97a_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Fbanks-cautious-in-providing-smaller-loans-of-less-than-rs-50000-to-new-to-credit-customers-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20number%20of%20defaulters%20increased%20to%2032.9%25%20in%20the%20personal%20loans%20segment%20as%20on%20April%2021%2C%202023%2C%20compared%20with%2031.4%25%2