ting.%20They%20are%20part%20of%20the%20special%20student%20cell%20established%20in%20Kota%20on%2024%20June%202023%2C%20which%20has%20a%2024%C3%977%20helpline%20with%20three%20numbers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20questions%20like%20is%20anything%20bothering%20them%2C%20do%20they%20really%20want%20to%20become%20an%20engineer%20or%20a%20doctor%20or%20if%20they%20able%20to%20understand%20what%20is%20being%20taught%20in%20class%20to%20other%20basic%20questions%20like%20do%20they%20like%20the%20food%20being%20served%20in%20the%20mess%2C%20these%20officers%20establish%20a%20rapport%20with%20the%20students%20to%20identify%20if%20they%20are%20at%20risk%20or%20if%20they%20are%20doing%20okay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20team%20is%20working%20with%20students%2C%20identifying%20mental%20health%20issues%2C%20and%20just%20offering%20a%20listening%20ear%20to%20them.%20We%20look%20for%20red%20flags%20or%20symptoms%20of%20depression%20when%20we%20interact%20with%20students.%20We%20speak%20to%20hostel%20wardens%2C%20mess%20staff%2C%20%3Cem%3Edabbawalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20understand%20which%20students%20are%20not%20eating%20properly%2C%20who%20is%20returning%20their%20tiffins%20without%20finishing.%20Food%20is%20a%20very%20important%20factor%20for%20these%20children.%20Once%20we%20identify%20these%20children%2C%20we%20speak%20one%20on%20one%20and%20guide%20them%20to%20counsellors%20in%20certain%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Thakur.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20cell%20also%20has%20a%20control%20room%20where%20police%20personnel%20are%20assigned%20to%20speak%20to%20callers.%20The%20ASP%20states%20that%20they%20receive%20almost%207%20calls%20everyday%20from%20students%20facing%20mental%20health%20issues.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20received%20over%20500%20serious%20calls%20in%20less%20than%20four%20months%2C%20highlighting%20how%20dire%20the%20situation%20is%20in%20Kota.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShashi%20Prakash%20Singh%2C%20a%20NEET%20coaching%20teacher%2C%20is%20on%20a%20sabbatical%20now%20to%20solely%20focus%20on%20counselling%20students.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20these%20suicides%20are%20an%20indicator%20of%20a%20larger%20mental%20health%20issue%20amongst%20students.%20He%20adds%20that%20the%20issues%20he%20has%20noticed%20are%20born%20broadly%20out%20of%20a%20language%20barrier%2C%20financial%20burden%20and%2For%20a%20lack%20of%20career%20counselling.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20met%20a%20girl%20from%20rural%20Bihar%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20come%20here%20but%20was%20sent%20as%20some%20relative%20of%20hers%20had%20cracked%20the%20NEET%20after%20coaching%20in%20Kota.%20She%20was%20bogged%20down%20by%20the%20financial%20and%20familial%20pressure%20of%20it%20all.%20Coming%20from%20a%20Hindi-medium%20school%2C%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20anything.%20She%20felt%20awkward%20in%20the%20hostels%20as%20most%20people%20spoke%20in%20English%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20confided%20in%20her%20parents%20about%20her%20inability%20to%20understand%20what%20was%20being%20taught%20and%20expressed%20her%20desire%20to%20come%20back%2C%20her%20parents%20heard%20none%20of%20it.%20Singh%20says%20that%20her%20parents%20told%20her%2C%20%E2%80%9CEither%20clear%20the%20NEET%20or%20we%20will%20marry%20you%20off%20next%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20mental%20burden%20on%20girls%20is%20much%20more%20than%20boys%2C%20according%20to%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20deeply%20disturbed%20by%20the%20rising%20student%20suicides.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBoys%20will%20be%20asked%20to%20look%20after%20the%20family%20business%2C%20be%20it%20a%20small%20shop%20or%20a%20farm.%20Girls%20are%20not%20even%20given%20that%20option.%20They%20are%20asked%20to%20clear%20the%20entrance%20or%20threatened%20with%20the%20punishment%20of%20marriage%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20parents%20must%20tell%20their%20children%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20okay%20to%20fail%2C%20and%20to%20let%20them%20choose%20other%20career%20options.%20Telling%20a%20barely%2015-year-old%20child%20that%20one%20exam%20is%20the%20do-all%20of%20their%20life%20leads%20to%20catastrophic%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20child%20will%20try%20and%20reach%20out%20for%20help%20about%20a%20hundred%20times%20before%20they%20take%20that%20step.%20We%20must%20address%20this%20problem%20as%20a%20society%20and%20help%20children%20battle%20depression.%20Everyone%20from%20parents%2C%20teachers%2C%20government%20bodies%20must%20preach%20that%20mental%20health%20is%20as%20important%20as%20physical%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20child%20tells%20a%20parent%20or%20teacher%20that%20they%20are%20not%20okay%2C%20one%20must%20address%20it%20immediately%20and%20talk%20to%20them.%20Just%20like%20you%20take%20your%20child%20to%20a%20doctor%20when%20they%20have%20a%20fever%2C%20take%20them%20to%20a%20psychologist%20too%20when%20they%20are%20low%20or%20depressed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98It%E2%80%99s%20okay%20to%20fail%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FA-students-room-in-Kota-min-1698068033.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20student%20spends%2015%20hours%20a%20day%20studying%20in%20Kota%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FA-students-room-in-Kota-min-1698068033.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FA-students-room-in-Kota-min-1698068033-238x300.jpeg%20238w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FA-students-room-in-Kota-min-1698068033-500x631.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FA-students-room-in-Kota-min-1698068033-768x970.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FA-students-room-in-Kota-min-1698068033-150x189.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332823%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221212%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20student%20spends%2015%20hours%20a%20day%20studying%20in%20Kota.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20problems%20faced%20by%20students%20can%20be%20split%20into%20three%20categories%20%E2%80%94%20parental%20expectations%2C%20the%20market%20of%20coaching%20classes%20and%20the%20education%20system.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECompetitive%20exams%20are%2C%20at%20its%20core%2C%20established%20to%20find%20the%20best%20candidate.%20They%20should%20not%20be%20treated%20like%20board%20exams.%20Only%20a%20few%20get%20selected.%20But%20what%20happens%20to%20the%20other%20children%3F%20Do%20we%20speak%20to%20them%20about%20what%20else%20they%20can%20do%3F%20Do%20we%20tell%20them%20it%E2%80%99s%20okay%20to%20fail%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F54484%2Fstudent-suicide-iit-jee-kota%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudents%20at%20Kota%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20all%20school%20toppers%2C%20some%20of%20the%20brightest%20young%20minds%20of%20the%20country.%20They%20are%20not%20used%20to%20failure.%20The%20coaching%20system%20here%20divides%20them%20into%20ranks%20and%20offers%20handsome%20rewards%20to%20the%20toppers.%20They%20use%20children%20as%20a%20commodity%20and%20their%20parents%20put%20all%20their%20hopes%20and%20pressures%20on%20their%20children.%20But%2C%20what%20can%20a%20child%20do%20in%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%20asks%20Thakur.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWithout%20having%20a%20capacity%20or%20the%20facility%20to%20handle%20stress%2C%20children%20get%20flustered.%20Even%20adults%20struggle%20with%20managing%20stress%2C%20how%20will%20the%20young%20kids%20fare%20then%3F%20Everyone%20is%20a%20competitor%20and%20the%20parents%20go%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20send%20their%20wards%20to%20Kota%2C%20where%20the%20coaching%20institutes%20have%20very%20high%20fees.%20Different%20reports%20suggest%20that%20the%20Kota%20coaching%20market%20generates%20more%20than%20Rs%206%2C000%20crores%20per%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERavi%20(name%20changed)%20came%20to%20Kota%20in%20June%202023.%20The%2016-year-old%E2%80%99s%20family%20owns%20a%20small%20grocery%20store%20in%20Kanpur%20and%20his%20father%20wanted%20him%20to%20become%20an%20engineer%20as%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20become%20one.%20He%20was%20raised%20with%20the%20expectations%20of%20studying%20in%20an%20IIT%20and%20being%20the%20harbinger%20of%20hope%20for%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20many%20friends%2C%20he%20says%2C%20and%20finds%20it%20difficult%20to%20adjust%20to%20this%2024%C3%977%20study%20environment%20where%20relaxation%20is%20hard%20to%20come%20by.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20my%20first%20time%20away%20from%20home%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20an%20introvert.%20I%20was%20a%20topper%20in%20my%20school%2C%20but%20so%20is%20everyone%20else%20here.%20The%20pressure%20is%20a%20lot.%20My%20parents%20have%20borrowed%20money%20to%20send%20me%20here%20and%20I%20know%20that%20they%20are%20doing%20all%20this%20to%20get%20me%20into%20an%20IIT.%20But%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20sure%20if%20I%E2%80%99ll%20get%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ravi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2FAED-20.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20still%20from%20the%20documentary%20'An%20Engineered%20Dream'.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2FAED-20.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2FAED-20-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2FAED-20-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2FAED-20-768x402.jpg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-252008%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20the%20documentary%20%E2%80%98An%20Engineered%20Dream%E2%80%99.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20race%20to%20the%20top%2C%20mental%20health%20is%20often%20ignored.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20the%20work%20of%20the%20police%20student%E2%80%99s%20cell%2C%20counsellors%20and%20teachers%20like%20Singh%20is%20crucial.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20may%20be%20life%20saving.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20student%E2%80%99s%20cell%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20over%2080%2C000%20students%20so%20far%2C%20according%20to%20Thakur.%20They%20interact%20with%20teachers%2C%20hostel%20wardens%2C%20PG%20owners%2C%20mess%20staff%20and%20Thakur%20himself%20spends%20many%20evenings%20at%20different%20hostels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20trying%20to%20bring%20a%20positive%20change.%20Now%2C%20students%20know%20that%20they%20can%20reach%20out%20to%20us.%20Hostel%20wardens%20and%20mess%20staff%20are%20the%20most%20important%20link%20for%20us.%20They%20can%20observe%20any%20small%20change%20in%20a%20child%2C%20and%20we%20ask%20them%20to%20report%20it%20to%20us%20immediately.%20Even%20what%20seems%20like%20a%20small%20problem%2C%20say%20of%20food%2C%20is%20resolved%20immediately.%20We%20also%20ask%20coaching%20classes%20to%20take%20extra%20lessons%20if%20a%20child%20tells%20us%20that%20he%20or%20she%20is%20unable%20to%20understand%20a%20concept%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Thakur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Life%20is%20bigger%20than%20one%20exam%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkota3-1698068081.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shashi%20Prakash%20Singh%20with%20students%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkota3-1698068081.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkota3-1698068081-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkota3-1698068081-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkota3-1698068081-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkota3-1698068081-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332825%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShashi%20Prakash%20Singh%20with%20his%20students.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3EHarsh%20Rajput%20came%20to%20Kota%20as%20he%20wants%20to%20get%20into%20an%20IIT.%20He%20is%20one%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98droppers%E2%80%99%2C%20who%20make%20up%20a%20huge%20chunk%20of%20students%20in%20the%20city.%20They%20drop%20a%20year%20out%20of%20college%20to%20just%20focus%20on%20clearing%20the%20entrance%20exam.%20Many%20students%20like%20Harsh%20attempt%20the%20entrance%20exam%2C%20be%20it%20NEET%20or%20JEE%2C%20and%20if%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20clear%2C%20they%20come%20here%20the%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20classes%20for%20even%20longer%20hours%2C%20and%20their%20days%20stretch%20for%2015%20hours%20of%20self-study%20and%20classes%2C%20as%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20board%20exams%20to%20concentrate%20on%20as%20well.%20This%20crushing%20routine%20and%20pressure%20to%20perform%20leads%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20anxiety.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20common%20problems%20Thakur%20and%20his%20team%20hear%20on%20the%20ground%20include%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20unable