e%20surviving%20on%20a%20rationed%20quantity%20of%20200%20litres%20of%20this%20filthy%20water%20for%207-8%20days%20per%20family%20and%20were%20absurdly%20grateful%20for%20it.%20It%20was%20beyond%20comprehension%20for%20someone%20who%20had%20never%20witnessed%20or%20suffered%20such%20scarcity%20in%20her%20life%20and%20she%20knew%20she%20had%20no%20option%20but%20to%20vest%20herself%20more%20fully%20into%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20she%20completed%20her%20work%20in%2048%20villages%20in%20Beed%2C%20Nutanben%20made%20her%20way%20to%20Jalna%20in%20July-August%202016%2C%20where%20she%20began%20working%20with%20her%20NGO%20%E2%80%98Samast%20Mahajan%E2%80%99%2C%20where%20she%20is%20a%20trustee%20based%20out%20of%20Mumbai%2C%20on%20desilting%20water%20bodies%20and%20rejuvenating%20water%20sources%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20local%20communities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20675px)%20100vw%2C%20675px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC01286_11zon-1697801665.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20locals%20in%20Jalna%20contributed%20their%20bit%20by%20providing%20the%20diesel.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC01286_11zon-1697801665.jpg%20675w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC01286_11zon-1697801665-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC01286_11zon-1697801665-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC01286_11zon-1697801665-150x112.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332692%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22506%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20locals%20in%20Jalna%20contributed%20their%20bit%20by%20providing%20the%20diesel.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-