s%20in%20cases%20where%20the%20entire%20funding%20is%20provided%20by%20the%20government.%20And%20the%20answer%20is%20%E2%80%93%20it%20takes%20both%20hands%20to%20clap.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20has%20been%20seen%20time%20and%20again%2C%20the%20projects%20that%20work%20best%20are%20those%20where%20the%20private%20and%20public%20sector%20come%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20a%20former%20NITI%20Aayog%20official.%20He%20says%20that%20the%20private%20or%20civil%20society%20players%20bring%20efficiencies%20and%20levels%20of%20competence%20that%20government%20players%20often%20lack.%20Chandra%20echoes%20this%20sentiment%20in%20reverse%20by%20saying%20that%20the%20scale%20government%20can%20provide%2C%20no%20private%20sector%20player%20can%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20even%20while%20the%20state%20government%20is%20willing%20to%20finance%20almost%20the%20entire%20effort%2C%20the%20A.T.E.%20CF%20identifies%2C%20monitors%20and%20assists%20the%20NGOs%20that%20work%20on%20the%20ground.%20It%20has%20also%20lent%20its%20technology%20app%20to%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20to%20collect%20real%20time%20data%20on%20all%20the%20water%20rejuvenation%20sites%20across%20the%20state%20from%20the%20Mantralaya%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20to%20prioritise%20where%20such%20work%20needs%20to%20commence%20right%20away.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20foundation%20also%20provides%20regular%20weekly%20training%20for%20the%20nodal%20government%20officers%20with%20use%20of%20the%20app%20and%20any%20glitches%20that%20may%20arise.%20Besides%20setting%20up%20a%20project%20management%20unit%2C%20the%20foundation%E2%80%99s%20chief%20operating%20officer%20(COO)%20Gayatri%20Nair%20Lobo%2C%20has%20made%2024%20field%20trips%20to%20six%20states%20%E2%80%93%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Jharkhand%20and%20Karnataka%20since%20April%202022%20alone.%20In%20a%20country%20as%20vast%2C%20diverse%20and%20complex%20as%20India%2C%20very%20li